hadiths[345]{hadithnumber,text}:
2092,"Hazrat Talha bin Ubedullah (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke eik bikhrey baalon wala Erabi (dehati) Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key paas aaya aur kehney laga : aey Allah key Rasool ! mujhey bataiye, Allah Taala ney mujh par kitni namazein farz ki hain? aap ney farmaya : paanch namazein illa ye ke to khushi sey mazeed padhey. us ney kaha : mujhey bataiye, Allah Taala ney mujh par rozey kitney farz kiye hain? aap ney farmaya : maah Ramzan key rozey , magar ye ke to khushi sey zayed rakhey. us ney kaha : mujhey bataiye, Allah Taala ney mujh par kitni Zakat farz ki hai? to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney usey Islam (aur Zakat ) key (tafsili) ehkam bataey. wo kehney laga : qism us zaat ki jisney aap ko izzat bakhshi! main Allah Taala key muqarrar karda faraaiz sey na zayed kuch karunga aur na un mein kami karunga. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : agar ye apni baat par pakka raha to kamiyab ho jaeyga ya jannat mein dakhil ho jaeyga."
2093,Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke hamen Quran Majeed mein is baat sey rok diya gaya tha ke hum Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) sey ziyada sawalat karen to hamari ye khahish hoti thi ke badwi logon mein sey koi samajh daar shakhs aaye aur aap sey sawalaat kerey. ittifaaq se (eik din ) eik badwi aaya aur kehney laga : aey Muhammad ! aap ka qaasid hamarey paas aaya aur us ney bataya ke aap kehtey hain ke Allah Taala ney aap ko Rasool banaya hai. aap ney farmaya is ney sach kaha. us ( badwi ) ney kaha : to aasmano ko kis ney paida kya ? farmaya : Allah Taala ney. us ney kaha : zamin ko kis ney banaya ? farmaya : Allah Taala ney. us ney kaha : zamin mein pahad kis ney nasab kiye ? aap ney farmaya : Allah Taala ney. us ney kaha : zamin mein manaafe kis ney rakhey? aap ney farmaya : Allah Taala ney. us ney kaha : qism hai us zaat ki jisney aasman o zamin paida kiye aur zamin mein pahad nasab kiye aur dusrey manaafe rakhey ! kya Allah Taala ney aap ko ( Rasool bana kar) bheja hai? aap ney farmaya : haan. us ney kaha : aur aap key qaasid ney kaha hai ke hum par eik din raat mein paanch namazein farz hain? aap ney farmaya is ney sach kaha. us ney kaha : qism us zaat ki jisney aap ko Rasool banaya ! kya Allah Taala ney aap ko unka hukm diya hai? farmaya : haan. us ney kaha : aur aap key qaasid ney kaha hai ke hum par hamarey maalon ki Zakat bhi wajib hai. farmaya is ney sach kaha. us ney kaha : qism us zaat ki jisney aap ko Rasool banaya ! kya Allah Taala ney aap ko uska hukm diya hai? aap ney farmaya : haan. us ney kaha : aur aap key qaasid ney kaha hai ke hum par har saal maah Ramzan key rozey farz hain? farmaya is ney sach kaha. us ney kaha : qism us zaat ki jisney aap ko Rasool banaya ! kya Allah Taala ney aap ko ye hukm diya hai? aap ney farmaya : haan. us ney kaha : aur aap key qaasid ney kaha hai ke jis shakhs ko baitullah tak pahunchney ki taqat ho is par Haj bhi farz hai. aap ney farmaya is ney sach kaha. us ney kaha : qism us zaat ki jisney aap ko Rasool banaya ! kya Allah Taala ney aap ko us ka hukm diya hai? aap ney farmaya : haan. us ney kaha : to phir us zaat ki qism jisney aap ko bar-haq Nabi banaya! main na un par izafa karunga aur na un mein kami karunga. jab wo wapas muda to aap ney farmaya : Allah ki qasam! agar ye apni baat par pakka raha to laziman jannat mein dakhil hoga.
2094,"Hazrat Anas bin Malik (Raziallahu anhu) farmatey hain ke eik dafa hum masjid mein bethey they ke eik aadmi oont par sawar ho kar aaya. us ney oont ko masjid mein bitha diya, phir us ka ghutna baandh diya aur kehney laga : tum mein sey Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) kon hain? Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) logon key darmiyan bethey they. hamney kaha : ye safed chehrey waley shakhs jo tek laga kar bethey hain. to wo shakhs (aap sey mukhatib ho kar) kehney laga : aey ibn abdul-Muttalib ! Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : baat kar main tujhey jawab dunga. (yani main teri baaten sun raha hun. ) us aadmi ney kaha : aey Muhammad ! main aap sey kuch baaten poochhney laga hun aur main sakht alfaz mein poochhunga to aap narazi mehsus na farmaiyega. aap ney farmaya : jo dil chahey poochh. us ney kaha : main aap sey aap key aur pehley tamam logon key rab ka wasta dey kar poochhta hun ke kya Allah Taala ney aap ko tamam logon ki taraf Rasool banaya hai? Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : Allah ki qasam! haan. us ney kaha : main aap sey Allah Taala ka wasta dey kar poochhta hun : kya Allah Taala ney aap ko hukm diya hai ke hum din-raat mein paanch namazein padha keren? Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : Allah ki qism ! haan. us ney kaha : to main aap ko Allah Taala ka wasta dey kar poochhta hun : kya Allah Taala ney aap ko saal mein sey us mahiney ( Ramzanul-Mubarak ) key rozey rakhney ka hukm diya hai? farmaya : Allah ki qism ! haan. us ney kaha : main aap sey Allah Taala ka wasta dey kar sawal karta hun : kya Allah Taala ney aap ko hukm diya hai ke aap hamarey maal daar logon sey Zakat ley kar hamarey gharib logon mein baant den ? Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : Allah ki qism ! haan. us aadmi ney kaha : main un tamam chizon par eman lata hun jo aap laye hain aur main apni qom ki taraf sey qaasid o numaainda hun. mera naam zamaam bin Solba hai aur main qabila Saad bin Bakr sey talluq rakhta hun. Yaqub bin Ibrahim ney Esa bin Hammad ki mukhalifat ki hai."
2095,"Hazrat Anas bin Malik (Raziallahu anhu) farmatey hain ke hum eik dafa Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key paas masjid mein bethey they ke eik aadmi oont par sawar ho kar aaya. us ney usey masjid mein bitha diya, phir uska ghutna baandha, phir kehney laga : tum mein sey Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) kon hain? us waqt aap logon key darmiyan tek lagaey bethey they. to hamney us sey kaha : ye roshan chehrey waley shakhs jo tek laga kar bethey hain. wo aap sey mukhatib ho kar kehney laga : aey ibn abdul-Muttalib ! aap ney farmaya : mainey tujhey jawab diya hai. ( meri teri baat sun raha hun. ) us ney kaha : aey Muhammad ! main aap sey kuch sawal karna chahta hun aur wo sawalaat mein sakht alfaz mein karunga. aap ney farmaya : jo ji chahey poochh. us ney kaha : main aap ko aap key aur aap sey pehley logon key rab ka wasta dey kar poochhta hun, kya Allah Taala ney aapko tamam logon key liye Rasool banaya hai? Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : Allah ki qasam! haan. us ney kaha : main aap sey Allah Taala ka wasta dey kar poochhta hun, kya Allah Taala ney aap ko hukm diya hai ke saal key us mahiney key rozey rakhen? Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : Allah ki qism ! haan. us ney kaha : main aap sey Allah Taala ka wasta dey kar poochhta hun, kya Allah Taala ney aap ko ye hukm diya hai ke aap hamarey maal daar logon sey Zakat ley kar hamarey gharib logon mein baant den ? Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : Allah ki qism ! haan. wo aadmi kehney laga : main un ehkam par eman lata hun jo aap laye hain. aur main apni qom ka qaasid o numaainda hun. aur mera naam zamaam bin Solba hai. mein qabila Saad bin Bakr sey talluq rakhta hun. Ubedullah bin umr ney Leis bin Saad ki mukhalifat ki hai."
2096,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) farmatey hain ke eik dafa Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) apney sahaba kiram Raziallahu anhum key sath they ke eik badwi shakhs aaya aur kehney laga : tum mein ibn abdul-Muttalib kon hain? unhoney kaha : ye surkh o safed ( gorey ) chehrey waley jo tek lagaey bethey hain. to usney (aap sey mukhatib ho kar) kaha ke main aap sey kuch sawal karna chahta hun aur main ye sawalaat sakht alfaz mein karunga. aap ney farmaya : jo ji chahta hai poochh. us ney kaha : main aap sey aap key aur aap sey pehley aur baad waley logon key rab ka wasta dey kar poochhta hun : kya Allah Taala ney aap ko Rasool banaya hai? aap ney farmaya : Allah ki qism ! haan. us ney kaha : main aap ko Allah ka wasta dey kar poochhta hun, kya Allah Taala ney aap ko hukm diya hai ke aap har din, raat mein paanch namazein padha keren? aap ney farmaya : Allah ki qism ! haan. us ney kaha : main aap ko usi zaat ka wasta dey kar poochhta hun : kya Allah Taala ney aap ko hukm diya hai ke hamarey maal daar logon sey Zakat ley kar gharib logon mein taqseem kar diya keren? aap ney farmaya : Allah ki qism ! haan. us ney kaha : main aapko usi zaat ka wasta dey kar poochhta hun : kya Allah Taala ney aap ko hukm diya hai ke baara mahinon mein sey us mahiney ( Ramzanul-Mubarak ) key rozey rakha keren? aap ney farmaya : Allah ki qism ! haan. us ney kaha : main Allah Taala ka wasta dey kar aap sey poochhta hun, kya Allah Taala ney aap ko hukm diya hai ke jo shakhs baitullah tak pahunch sakta ho, wo us ka Haj karey ? aap ney farmaya : Allah ki qism ! haan. us ney kaha : main eman lata hun aur aap ki tasdeeq karta hun aur mera naam Zamam bin Solba hai."
2097,Hazrat Abdullah bin Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) farmaya kartey they ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) sab logon sey ziyada sakhi they aur aap Ramzanul-Mubarak mein ziyada sakhawat kartey they jab Jibril alehissalam aap sey miltey they. aur Ramzanul-Mubarak key mahiney mein Jibril alehissalam har raat aap sey miltey aur aap sey Quran Majeed ka door kya kartey they. jab Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) sey Jibril alehissalam miltey to aap chhodi hui ( tez ) huwa sey bhi badh kar sakhawat farmatey they.
2098,"Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) farmati hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney koi lanat aisi nahin ki jo qabile-zikr ho. aur jab Hazrat Jibril alehissalam sey door karney ka waqt qarib hota to aap ( tez ) chhodi hui huwa usey badh kar sakhawat farmaya kartey they. Imam abu-Abdur-Rehman ( Nasai) (Rahmatullahi Alaih) bayan kartey hain ke ye riwayat ghalat hai, sahih riwayat Yunus bin Yazid ki hai. us hadees key raawi ney do hadeeson ko gadmad kar diya hai."
2099,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jab maah Ramzanul-Mubarak shuru ho jata hai to jannat key darwazey khol diye jatey hain aur aag key darwazey band kar diye jatey hain aur shayatin jakad diye jatey hain."
2100,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey marwi hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jab Ramzanul-Mubarak shuru hota hai to jannat key darwazey khol diye jatey hain aur aag key darwazey band kar diye jatey hain aur shayatin jakad diye jatey hain."
2101,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey manqul hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jab Ramzanul-Mubarak shuru hota hai to jannat key darwazey khol diye jatey hain aur jahannam key darwazey band kar diye jatey hain aur shayatin qaid kar diye jatey hain."
2102,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey marwi hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jab Ramzanul-Mubarak aata hai to rehmat key darwazey khol diye jatey hain aur jahannam key darwazey band kar diye jatey hain aur shayatin zanjeer band kar diye jatey hain."
2103,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jab Ramzanul-Mubarak aata hai to jannat key darwazey khol diye jatey hain aur aag key darwazey band kar diye jatey hain aur shayatin jakad diye jatey hain. us riwayat ko Zohri sey ibn Is-haq ney bhi bayan kya hai. ( jo aagey aa rahi hai )."
2104,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey marwi hai, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jab maah Ramzanul-Mubarak aata hai to jannat key darwazey khol diye jatey hain aur aag key darwazey band kar diye jatey hain aur shayatin ko zanjeeren laga di jati hain. Imam abu-Abdur-Rehman ( Nasai) (Rahmatullahi Alaih) bayan kartey hain ke ye, yani ibn Is-haq ki hadees khata hai kyonkey ibn Is-haq ney ye hadees Zohri sey nahin suni. durust wohi hai jo hum peechey zikr kar chukey hain."
2105,"Hazrat Anas bin Malik (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : ye Ramzanul-Mubarak tumharey paas tashrif la chuka hai, is mein jannat key darwazey khol diye jatey hain aur aag key darwazey band kar diye jatey hain aur shayatin qaid kar diye jatey hain. Imam abu-Abdur-Rehman ( Nasai) (Rahmatullahi Alaih) farmatey hain : ye hadees sahih nahin. (yani Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) key bajaey Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) ka zikr sahih nahin."
2106,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) qiyame-Ramzan (taravih) ki targheeb detey they lekin zaruri qarar na detey they, neez aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jab Ramzanul-Mubarak aata hai to jannat key darwazey khol diye jatey hain, bhadakti aag key darwazey band kar diye jatey hain aur shayatin jakad diye jatey hain. (Mamar key shagrid) ibne-mubarak ney us riwayat ko mursal (munqata) bayan kya hai. ( yani abu-Salma ka wasta zikr nahin kya. )"
2107,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey manqul hai, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jab Ramzanul-Mubarak shuru hota hai to rehmat key darwazey khol diye jatey hain, jahannam key darwazey band kar diye jatey hain aur shayatin qaid kar diye jatey hain."
2108,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey marwi hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : tumharey paas eik ba-barkat mahina Ramzan aa chuka hai, Allah Taala ney tum par us mahiney key rozey farz qarar diye hain. is mein aasman key darwazey khol diye jatey hain, jahannam key darwazey band kar diye jatey hain aur sarkash shayatin ko toq pahna diye jatey hain. us main eik raat hai jo hazar maah sey behtar hai. jo us raat ki neki ( ibadat ) sey mehroom raha, wo haqiqat mein mehrum shakhs hai."
2109,Hazrat Arfaja sey manqul hai ke hum Hazrat Utba bin Farqad (Raziallahu anhu) ki bimar pursi key liye gaey. wahan hum Ramzanul-Mubarak ka tazkira karney lagey. unhoney kaha : tum kya zikr kar rahey ho? hamney arz kya : maah Ramzan ka tazkira kar rahey hain. farmaya : mainey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ko farmatey suna hai is maah mubarak mein jannat key darwazey khol diye jatey hain aur aag key darwazey band kar diye jatey hain aur shayatin jakad diye jatey hain aur har raat eik aelan karney wala aelan karta hai : aey neki key talabgar ! idhar aa. aur aey gunah key talabgar! ruk ja. abu-Abdur-Rehman (Imam Nasai) (Rahmatullahi Alaih) bayan kartey hain : ye hadees ghalat hai.
2110,"Hazrat Arfaja bayan kartey hain ke main eik ghar mein tha jis mein Hazrat Utba bin Farqad (Raziallahu anhu) bhi they. to mainey eik hadees bayan karney ka irada kya. ( wahan ) Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key sahaba mein sey eik sahab they, lihaza wo meri bajaey hadees bayan karney key ziyada haq daar they. unhoney Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) sey hadees bayan farmaai ke aap ney Ramzanul-Mubarak key barey mein bayan farmaya : is mein aasman key darwazey khol diye jatey hain, aag key darwazey band kar diye jatey hain, har sarkash shetan ko bediyon mein jakad diya jata hai aur har raat eik aelan karney wala aelan karta hai : aey neki key talabgar! aagey aa aur aey shar key talabgar! ruk ja."
2111,"Hazrat abu-Bakra (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : tum mein sey koi shakhs ye na kahey ke mainey purey Ramzan key rozey rakhey ya mainey tamam raaton ka qiyam kya. (raawi kehta hai) main nahin janta ke aap ney apney munh tareef ko bura samjha ya is liye ke insan sey ghaflat aur neend ka ho jana lazimi Amr hai. ye alfaz Ubedullah (bin Saeed) key hain."
2112,Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) batatey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney ansaar ki eik aurat ko farmaya : jab Ramzanul-Mubarak shuru ho jaey to is mein Umra kar lena kyonkey Ramzanul-Mubarak mein Umra Haj key barabar hai.
2113,"Hazrat Kureb bayan kartey hain ke mujhey Hazrat Umme-Fazal (Raziallahu anha) ney (kisi kaam key liye) ilaaqa Sham mein Hazrat Muawiya (Raziallahu anhu) (Ameerul-momeneen ) key paas bheja. main Sham gaya aur unka kaam pura kiya. main abhi Sham hi mein tha ke Ramzanul-Mubarak ka chaand tulu ho gaya. mainey b-zaate-khud Jumey ki raat chaand dekha, phir main maahe Ramzanul-Mubarak key aakhir mein Madina Munawra wapis aaya to Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ney chaand ka zikr kartey huye mujh sey puchha ke tum ney ( Ramzanul-Mubarak ka) chaand kab dekha tha? mainey kaha : hamney jume ki raat dekha tha. wo farmaney lagey : tu ney khud Jumey ki raat dekha tha? mainey kaha : ji haan. dusrey logon ney bhi dekha tha, phir logon ney aur Hazrat Muawiya (Raziallahu anhu) ney roza rakha. aap ney farmaya hamney to haftey ki raat dekha tha. hum to rozey rakhtey rahengey yahan tak ke tees purey ho jaeyn ya chaand dekh lein. mainey kaha : kya aap Hazrat Muawiya (Raziallahu anhu) aur unkey sathiyon key chaand dekh leney ko kafi nahin samajhtey? unhoney kaha : nahin, hamein Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney yehi hukm diya hai."
2114,Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke eik erabi (dehati) Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key paas aaya aur kehney laga : mainey chaand dekha hai. farmaya : to gawahi deta hai ke Allah Taala key siwa koi mabood nahin aur Hazrat Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) Allah Taala key bandey aur Rasool hain? us ney kaha : ji haan. to Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney aelan kar diya : roza rakho.
2115,Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke eik erabi (dehati) Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key paas aaya aur kehney laga : mainey aaj raat chaand dekha hai. aap ney farmaya : to gawahi deta hai ke Allah Taala key siwa koi mabood nahin aur Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) uskey bandey aur Rasool hain? us ney kaha : ji haan. aap ney farmaya : aey Bilal ! logon mein aelan kar do kal roza rakhen.
2116,Abu-Daawood (Umar bin Saad Hafri) ney Hazrat Sufiyan sey unhoney Simaak sey unhoney Hazrat ikrima sey ye riwayat mursal bayan ki hai.
2117,Abdullah ney Hazrat Sufiyan sey unhoney Simaak sey unhoney Hazrat Ikrima (Rahmatullahi Alaih) sey ye riwayat mursal bayan ki hai.
2118,Hazrat Husain bin Haris Jadli sey riwayat hai ke Hazrat Abdur-Rehman bin Zaid bin Khitab ney us din logon ko khitab kiya jis din Ramzanul-Mubarak hona mashkook tha. unhoney farmaya : main Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key sahaba kiram Raziallahu anhum key paas bethta raha hun aur un sey masaayel bhi poochhtey raha hun. unhoney mujhey bayan kiya hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : chaand dekh kar rozey rakhna shuru karo aur chaand dekh kar rozey rakhna band karo. aur chaand dekh kar hi Haj aur qurbani karo. agar chaand nazar na aaye to (mahiney key) tees din purey kar lo. aur agar do shakhs chaand dekhney ki gawahi den to bhi rozey rakhna shuru ya band kar do.
2119,Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : rozon ka aaghaz chaand dekh kar karo aur ikhtitaam bhi chaand dekh kar karo. agar badal hon (aur chaand nazar na aaye) to tees din purey karo.
2120,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey marwi hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : chaand dekh kar rozey rakhna shuru karo aur chaand dekh kar hi rozey rakhna band karo aur agar badal hon (aur chaand nazar na aaye) to mahina tees ka samjho."
2121,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey manqul hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jab tum ( Ramzanul-Mubarak ka) chaand dekh lo, tab rozey rakhna shuru karo aur jab tum (shawwaal ka) chaand dekh lo to rozey rakhna band kar do. agar badal hon (aur tumhen shawwaal ka chaand nazar na aaye) to tees rozey purey karo."
2122,Hazrat Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke mainey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ko farmatey suna : jab tum chaand dekho to rozey rakhna shuru kar do aur jab tum (shawwaal ka) chaand dekho to rozey rakhna band kar do. agar badal hon (aur chaand nazar na aaye) to is mahiney ko tees ka samjho.
2123,"Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney Ramzanul-Mubarak ka zikr farmaya to farmaney lagey : jab tak chaand na dekh lo, rozey rakhna shuru na karo. isi tarah rozey rakhna band na karo jab tak ( shawwaal ka) chaand na dekh lo. agar badal hon (aur chaand nazar na aaye ) to is mahiney ko tees din ka farz karo."
2124,"Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) sey manqul hai, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : tum rozey rakhna shuru na karo yahan tak ke ( Ramzanul-Mubarak ka) chaand dekh lo aur rozey rakhna band na karo yahan tak ke ( shawwaal ka) chaand dekh lo. agar chaand nazar na aaye to mahina tees ka banao."
2125,Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan farmatey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney chaand ka zikr kiya to farmaya : jab tum chaand dekho to rozey rakhna shuru kar do aur jab tum chaand dekho to rozey rakhna band kar do aur agar badal hon (aur chaand nazar na aaye ) to tees din purey karo.
2126,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : chaand dekh kar rozey rakho aur chaand dekh kar eid karo. agar chaand chhup jaey ( nazar na aaye ) to is mahiney ki ginti tees din mukammal karo."
2127,Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke mujhey us shakhs par tajjub hai jo maahe Ramzan shuru honey sey pehley roza rakhta hai jabkey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya hai : jab tum chaand dekho to phir roza rakho aur jab aglaa chaand dekho to rozey rakhna chhod do. agar chaand chhup jaey ( nazar na aaye ) to mahiney ki ginti tees din puri karo.
2128,"Hazrat Huzefa bin Yamaan (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : maahe-Ramzan sey pehley roza na rakho yahan tak ke roza rakhney sey pehley (Ramzanul-Mubarak ka) chaand dekh lo, warna (sho'baan key) tees din purey kar key roza rakho, phir tum rozey rakhtey raho yahan tak ke (shawwaal ka) chaand dekh lo ya chaand dekhney sey pehley tees din purey kar lo."
2129,"Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key eik sahabi (Raziallahu anhu) sey manqul hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : maah Ramzanul-Mubarak sey pehley rozey rakhna shuru na karo yahan tak ke ( Shoban ) key tees din purey karo ya ( Ramzan ka) chaand dekh lo, phir rozey rakhtey raho aur rozey rakhney band na karo yahan tak ke ( shawwaal ka) chaand dekh lo ya (Ramzanul-Mubarak key) tees rozey purey kar lo. Hujjaaj bin Irtaat ney is riwayat ko mursal zikr kiya hai (ke unhoney sahabi ka wasta hi khatam kar diya aur isey Rabaee ki riwayat bana diya, halanke wo sahabi nahin)."
2130,"Hazrat Rabaee sey riwayat hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jab tum (Ramzanul-Mubarak ka) chaand dekh lo to rozey shuru karo aur jab tum ( shawwaal ka) chaand dekh lo to rozey rakhna band kar do. agar badal hon (aur tumhen chaand nazar na aaye ) to Shoban key tees din purey karo, siwaey iske ke ye ke tum is sey pehley chaand dekh lo, phir tees din rozey rakho, siwaey iske ke ye ke is sey pehley chaand dekh lo."
2131,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan farmatey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : chaand dekh kar rozey rakho aur chaand dekh kar rozey khatam karo. agar tumharey aur chaand key darmiyan badal haael (rukawat) ho jaeyn (aur chaand nazar na aaye ) to maroof ginti ( tees din ) puri karo aur maah Ramzanul-Mubarak key shuru honey sey pehley roza na rakho."
2132,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) sey marwi hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : Ramzanul-Mubarak shuru honey sey pehley roza na rakho balke chaand dekh kar roza rakho aur chaand dekh kar hi rozey rakhney band karo. agar chaand nazar aaney mein badal rukawat ban jaeyn to tees din purey karo."
2133,Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) farmati hain ke (eik dafa) Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney (narazi ki bina par) qism kha li ke apni biwiyon key paas eik mahiney tak nahin jaunga. aap untees din tak isi haal mein rahey. (phir merey paas tashrif laye) mainey (yaad-dahani key taur par) arz kiya ke aap ney eik maah ki qism nahin khai thi mainey to untees din shumar kiye hain? Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : mahina untees din ka bhi hota hai.
2134,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke main lambey waqt sey khahish mand tha ke main Hazrat umr bin Khattab (Raziallahu anhu) sey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ki azwaje-mutahrat (paak biwiyon) mein sey un do aurton key barey mein poochhun jinkey barey mein Allah Taala ney farmaya : (اِنْ تَتُوْبَا اِلَی اللّٰہِ فَقَدْ صَغَتْ قُلُوْبُکُمَا), ''agar tum Allah Taala ki taraf ruju karo to ye nihayat munasib hai kyonkey tumharey dil kaj (tedhey) ho gaey hain.'' phir Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ney puri hadees bayan farmaai . us tafsili hadees mein Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) ney farmaya : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) us baat ki wajeh sey jisey Hazrat Hafsa (Raziallahu anha) ney Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) key samney faash ( zahir ) kar diya tha, untees din tak apni biwiyon sey juda rahey. Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ney farmaya : aap ney ( qism kha kar) farmaya tha : main apni biwiyon key paas eik mahiney tak nahin aaun ga . jis waqt Allah Taala ney aap ko yahudiyon ki baat batai to aap un par sakht naraz ho gaey they jab untees din guzar gaey to sab sey pehley aap Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) key paas tashrif ley gaey. Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) kehney lagen : aey Allah key Rasool ! aap ney to qism khai thi ke eik maah tak hamarey paas tashrif na laeyngey aur aaj to unteesween din ki subh hai. hamney ye din gin gin kar guzaarey hain. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : mahina untees ka bhi hota hai."
2135,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : merey paas Hazrat Jibril alehissalam aaye aur bataya ke mahina untees din ka bhi hota hai."
2136,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) sey manqul hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : mahina untees din ka bhi hota hai."
2137,"Hazrat Saad bin Abi Waqas (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney apney eik daste-mubarak ko dusrey par maara aur farmaya : kabhi mahina itna, itna aur itna bhi hota hai aur teesri dafa aap ney eik ungli kam kar li. (yani untees)."
2138,"Hazrat Saad (Raziallahu anhu) sey marwi hai, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : mahina kabhi itna, itna aur itna bhi hota hai (yani untees din ka). Yahya bin Saeed waghera ney is riwayat ko ba-wasta Ismail, Muhammad bin Saad sey (sahabi Rasool Saad bin Abi Waqas (Raziallahu anhu) key wastey key baghair) Nabi Akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) sey bayan kiya hai, yani mursalan."
2139,"Hazrat Muhammad bin Saad bin Abi Waqas sey riwayat hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : mahina itna, itna aur itna bhi hota hai. (hadees key raawi) Muhammad bin Ubaid ney apney dono haathon ki hatheliyan khol kar samney kin. teen dafa aisey kiya aur teesri dafa baain haath key angoothey ko band kar liya. Yahya bin Saeed kehtey hain : mainey Ismail sey puchha : kya Muhammad bin Saad ney is riwayat ko apney baap (Saad bin Abi waqaas) sey bayan kiya hai? unhoney kaha : nahin (balke mursalan bayan kiya hai)."
2140,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : mahina kabhi untees din ka aur kabhi tees din ka hota hai. jab tum chaand dekho to rozey rakhna shuru karo aur jab tum chaand dekho to rozey rakhna band kar do aur agar badal hon (aur chaand nazar na aaye) to (tees din ki) ginti puri karo."
2141,Hazrat Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke mainey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ko farmatey suna : mahina untees ka ( bhi hota ) hai.
2142,"Hazrat Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : hum ummi (anpadh) log hain. hum hisab kitab nahin jantey. mahina itna, itna aur itna hota hai. teen dafa haathon sey ishara farmaya yahan tak ke untees ho gaey."
2143,"Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) bayan farmatey hain, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : hum ummi (anpadh) log hain, hum hisab kitab nahin jantey. kabhi mahina itna, itna aur itna hota hai. teesri dafa aap ney angoothaa band farma liya (yani untees din ka). aur kabhi mahina itna, itna aur itna hota hai. yani purey tees din ka."
2144,"Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : mahina kabhi itna hota hai. Shoba ney Jabla bin Saheem ki naqal ki aur unhoney Hazrat Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu anhu) ki ke mahina untees din ka (bhi) hota hai. unhoney is tarah sey bayan kiya ke do dafa aap ney dono haathon ki puri ungliyan kholin aur teesri dafa eik ungli kam (band) kar li."
2145,"Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) sey manqul hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : mahina untees ka bhi hota hai."
2146,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Masood (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : sehri khaya karo, bilashuba sehri khaney mein barkat hai. Ubedullah bin Saeed ney is riwayat ko maqoof bayan kiya hai."
2147,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Masood (Raziallahu anhu) farmatey hain, sehri khao. (hadees ke raawi) Ubedullah ney kaha : main nahin janta iskey (sahih) alfaz kya hain?"
2148,"Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : sehri khaya karo, yaqinan is mein barkat hai."
2149,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey marwi hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : sehri khaya karo, bilashuba sehri khaney mein barkat hai."
2150,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke sehri khao, bilashuba sehri khaney mein barkat hai. Hazrat ibn Abi Laila ney is riwayat ko marfooa bayan kiya hai."
2151,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey manqul hai, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : sehri khao, bilashuba sehri khaney mein barkat hai."
2152,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey marwi hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : sehri khao, bilashuba sehri khaney mein barkat hai."
2153,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : sehri khao, yaqinan sehri khaney mein barkat hai. Imam abu-Abdur-Rehman (Nasai) (Rahmatullahi Alaih) bayan kartey hain ke Yahya bin Saeed ki is hadees ki sanad Hasan hai lekin ye riwayat munkir (ghalat) hai. mujhey khadsha (dar) hai ke ye ghalati Muhammad bin Fuzail sey hui hogi."
2154,"Hazrat Zarr bayan kartey hain ke hamney Hazrat Huzefa (Raziallahu anhu) sey puchha ke aap ney Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key sath sehri kis waqt khai? unhoney farmaya : din shuru honey hi ko tha, bas suraj tulu na huwa tha."
2155,"Hazrat Zarr bin Habish bayan kartey hain ke mainey Hazrat Huzefa (Raziallahu anhu) key sath sehri khai, phir hum namaz key liye nikley. jab hum masjid mein aaye to do rakaten padhin itney mein jamaat khadi ho gaee. sunnaton aur iqaamat key darmiyan bilkul maamuli fasla tha."
2156,Hazrat Sila bin Zufr bayan kartey hain ke mainey Hazrat Huzefa (Raziallahu anhu) key sath sehri khai. phir hum masjid ko chaley hamney Fajr ki do sunnaten padhin itney mein namaze Fajr ki iqaamat ho gaee to hamney farz namaz padhi.
2157,"Hazrat Zaid bin Sabit (Raziallahu anhu) sey manqul hai ke hamney Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key sath sehri khai, phir hum namaz key liye uthey. Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) ney farmaya : mainey puchha ke darmiyan mein kitna fasla tha? unhoney farmaya : itna ke aadmi pachas aayaten padh sakey."
2158,"Hazrat Zaid bin Sabit (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke hamney Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key sath sehri khai, phir hum namaz key liye uthey, mainey kaha … khayal kiya jata hai ke kehney waley Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) hain … darmiyan mein kitna fasla tha? unhon (Zaid (Raziallahu anhu)) ney farmaya : itna ke aadmi pachas aayaat padh sakey."
2159,"Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) aur Hazrat Zaid bin Sabit (Raziallahu anhu) ney (ikhattey) sehri khai, phir wo dono khadey huye aur subah ki namaz padhney lagey. (Qatada ney kaha : ) mainey Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) sey puchha : sehri sey farigh honey aur namaz shuru karney key darmiyan kitna fasla tha? unhoney farmaya : itna ke insan pachas aayaat padh sakey."
2160,Hazrat Abu Atiya sey riwayat hai ke mainey Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) sey arz kiya : hum mein Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key do sahabi mojud hain. un mein sey eik roza jaldi (aaftaab ghurub hotey hi) kholtey hain aur sehri takheer sey (aakhir waqt mein) khatey hain aur dusrey sahabi (ehtiyati taur par) iftaar der sey kartey hain aur sehri jaldi kha letey hain. wo farmaney lagen : un mein sey iftaar awwal waqt aur sehri aakhir waqt karney wala kon hai? mainey kaha : Hazrat Abdullah bin Masood (Raziallahu anhu). unhoney farmaya : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ka mamool bhi yehi tha.
2161,Hazrat Abu Atiya (Raziallahu anhu) sey manqul (naqal hui) hai ke mainey Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) sey arz kiya : hum mein do hazraat hain. un mein sey eik iftaari awwal waqt aur sehri aakhir waqt kartey hain aur dusrey sahab iftaari der sey aur sehri jaldi kar letey hain. aap ney farmaya : un mein sey iftaari awwal waqt aur sehri aakhir waqt mein kon karta hai? mainey kaha : Hazrat Abdullah bin Masood (Raziallahu anhu). unhoney farmaya : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) isi tarah kiya kartey they.
2162,"Hazrat Abu Atiya farmatey hain ke main aur Hazrat Masruq dono Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ki khidmat mein hazir huye to Hazrat Masruq ney un sey arz kiya : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key sahaba mein sey do aadmi hain, un mein sey koi bhi neki mein kotahi nahin karta magar un mein sey eik iftaari aur namaze Maghrib mein takheer (deri) kartey hain aur dusrey sahab iftaari aur namaze Maghrib mein jaldi kartey hain. Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ney puchha : un mein sey kon namaze Maghrib aur iftaari mein jaldi kartey hain? Hazrat Masruq ney kaha : Hazrat Abdullah bin Masood (Raziallahu anhu). Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ney farmaya : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) isi tarah kiya kartey they."
2163,Hazrat Abu Atiya sey marwi (riwayat hui) hai ke main aur Hazrat Masruq Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) key paas hazir huye aur hamney un sey kaha : aey Ummul-Mominin ! as-haabe Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) mein sey do aadmi hain. un mein sey eik iftaari aur namaze Maghrib jaldi ada kartey hain aur dusrey iftaari aur namaze Maghrib mein takheer (deri) kartey hain. farmaney lagin : un mein sey kon iftaari aur namaze Maghrib mein jaldi kartey hain? hamney kaha : Hazrat Abdullah bin Masood (Raziallahu anhu). unhoney farmaya : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ka tarze amal yehi tha. dusrey sahabi Hazrat Abu-Musa Ash-ari (Raziallahu anhu) they.
2164,"Rasool (Raziallahu anhu) ke eik sahabi sey riwayat hai ke main Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key paas hazir huwa to aap sehri tanaawul farma (kha) rahey they. aap ney farmaya : bilashuba sehri barkat hai jo Allah Taala ney tumhen ata farmaee hai, lihaza tum isey na chhodo."
2165,Hazrat Arbaaz bin Saariya (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke mainey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ko Ramzanul-Mubarak mein sehri ki dawat detey suna. aap farma rahey they : aao is mubarak khaney ki taraf.
2166,"Hazrat Miqdaam bin Maadikarb (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Nabi Akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : sehri ka khana khaya karo kyonkey ye ba-barkat khana hai."
2167,"Hazrat Khalid bin Ma'daan (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney eik aadmi sey farmaya : is ba-barkat khaney, yani sehri key liye aao."
2168,"Hazrat Amr bin Aas (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : hamarey aur ehle-kitab key rozey key darmiyan farq, sehri khana hai."
2169,"Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney sehri key waqt farmaya : aey Anas ! main roza rakhna chahta hun, mujhey kuchh khilao. main aap key paas kuchh khajuren aur eik pani ka bartan ley kar aaya aur ye Hazrat Bilal (Raziallahu anhu) key Azan (Azan awwal) kehney key baad ki baat hai, phir aap farmaney lagey : aey Anas ! koi aadmi dekho jo merey sath sehri khaye. main Hazrat Zaid bin Sabit (Raziallahu anhu) ko bula laya, wo aaye aur kehney lagey : mainey kuchh sattu pi liye hain aur mera irada roza rakhney ka hai. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : mera irada bhi roza rakhney ka hai. to unhoney aap key sath sehri khai, phir aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) uthey, do rakaten padhin aur phir namaz key liye nikal gaey."
2170,"Hazrat Bara bin Aazib (Raziallahu anhu) sey manqul hai ke (shuru shuru mein) musalmanon mein sey koi shakhs jab raat ko khana khaney sey pehley so jata tha to uskey liye kuchh bhi khana peena jayez na hota tha, na us raat aur na agley din yahan tak ke suraj ghurub ho jaey. (yehi soorate-haal rahi) yahan tak ke ye aayat utri :(وَکُلُوْا وَاشْرَبُوْا … مِنَ الْخَیْطِ الْاَسْوَدِ),''khao aur piyo yahan tak ke tumharey liye subah ki safed dhaari siyah dhaari sey wazeh (roshan) ho jaey. ye aayat Hazrat Abu-Qais bin Amr (Raziallahu anhu) key barey mein utri. wo Maghrib ki namaz key baad ghar walon key paas aaye, unka roza tha. kehney lagey : koi khaney ki chiz hai? un ki biwi ney kaha : khaney ki koi chiz bhi nahin lekin main ja kar khana talash karti hun. wo bahar chali gaeen aur wo let gaey, unhein neend aa gaee. wo wapis aayin to unhen sotey huye paya. unhin jagaya lekin wo kuchh na kha sakey, isi tarah raat guzari. agli subah phir roza tha yahan tak ke dophare hui to wo be-hosh ho gaey. aur ye is aayat key utarney sey pehley ki baat hai, to Allah Taala ney ye aayat unkey barey mein utaari."
2171,"Hazrat Adi bin Hatim (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke mainey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) sey Allah Taala key farman : (حَتّٰی یَتَبَیَّنَ لَکُمْ الْاَسْوَدِ), ''yahan tak ke tumharey liye safed dhaari siyah dhaari sey wazeh ho jaey."" key barey mein puchha. aap ney farmaya : is sey raat ki siyahi aur din ki safedi murad hai."
2172,"Hazrat ibne-Masood (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : Bilal raat ko Azan kehtey hain taake soey hueyn ko jagaeyn aur jaagey huey ko lautaaen aur Fajr is tarah nahin hoti. aur aap ney apni hatheli sey (oopper nichey) ishara kya. balke Fajr is tarah hoti hai. aur aap ney apni dono angusht shahadat sey daeyn baain ishara farmaya."
2173,"Hazrat Samura (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : Bilal ki Azan aur is safedi (Fajr) sey tumhen dhoka na lagey yahan tak ke Fajr is tarah daeyn baain phel jaey. Abu-Daawood (raawi) ney kaha : aur us (ustaad Shoba) ney apney dono haath khol kar daeyn baain khinch kar phelaey."
2174,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : maahe Ramzanul-Mubarak shuru honey sey pehley koi roza na rakho siwaey iske ke koi shakhs pehley khas din ka roza rakhta ho aur wo din aisey moqe par aa jaey."
2175,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ney khabar di ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : koi shakhs Ramzanul-Mubarak sey eik do din pehley roza na rakhey magar jo shakhs pehley sey kisi khas din ka roza rakhta hai, wo rakh sakta hai."
2176,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : maah Ramzanul-Mubarak sey eik do din pehley roza na rakho magar ye ke ittifaaq se wo din aa jaey jis ka koi shakhs pehley sey roza rakhney ka aadi ho. Imam abu-Abdur-Rehman (Nasai) (Rahmatullahi Alaih) ney farmaya : ye ghalati hai."
2177,"Abu-Salma kehtey hain ke Hazrat Umme-Salma (Raziallahu anha) ney farmaya : mainey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ko pay-dar-pay do maah key rozey rakhtey nahin dekha, albatta aap Shoban (key rozon) ko Ramzanul-Mubarak (key rozon) sey mila letey they."
2178,Hazrat Umme-Salma (Raziallahu anha) farmati hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) Shoban ( key rozon ) ko Ramzanul-Mubarak ( key rozon ) key sath mila letey they.
2179,Hazrat Abu-Salma bin Abdur-Rehman ney Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) sey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key (nafl) rozon key barey mein puchha to unhoney farmaya : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) kabhi (nafl) rozey rakhtey yahan tak ke hum kehtey they : aap naagha nahin kerengey. aur kabhi chhodey rehtey yahan tak ke hum kehtey : aap rozey nahin rakhengey. aap sara Shoban ya aksar Shoban rozey rakhtey they.
2180,"Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) sey marwi hai ke hum azwaje-mutahrat (paak biwiyon) mein sey kisi eik ko Ramzanul-Mubarak key kuchh rozey (haiz ki bina par) chhodney padtey they, wo un ki qaza nahin dey sakti thi yahan tak ke maahe-sho'baan aa jata. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) kisi mahiney mein itney rozey na rakhtey they jitney Shoban mein rakhtey they, sirf chand din chhod kar baqi rozey rakhtey they balke (yehi keh lijiye ke) sara mahina hi rozey rakhtey they."
2181,"Hazrat Abu-Salma bayan kartey hain ke : mainey Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) sey arz kiya ke mujhey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key (nafl) rozon key barey mein bataiye. farmaney lagin : aap (kabhi to is qadr) rozey rakhtey they ke hum kehtey they : ab rozey hi rakhtey rahengey. kabhi itney naaghey farmatey ke hum kehtey ke ab chhod hi diye hain. aur aap Shoban sey ziyada kisi mahiney mein (nafli) rozey na rakhtey they, (yun keh lijiye ke) sara Shoban hi rozey rakhtey they."
2182,Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) farmati hain ke : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) saal key kisi mahiney mein Shoban sey ziyada (nafl) rozey na rakhtey they. (yun samajhiye ke) pura Shoban hi rozey rakhtey they.
2183,Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) sey marwi hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) Shoban mein (bahut ziyada) rozey rakhtey they.
2184,Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) sey manqul (naqal hui) hai ke main to nahin jaanti ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney kabhi eik raat mein mukammal Quran Majeed padha ho ya kisi raat (shuru sey aakhir tak) musalsal namaz padhtey rahey hon ya Ramzanul-Mubarak key ilawa kisi mahiney key mukammal rozey rakhey hon.
2185,Hazrat Abdullah bin Shaqeeq sey manqul hai ke mainey Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) sey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key ( nafl ) rozon key barey mein puchha to unhoney farmaya : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) rozey rakhney lagtey to hum kehtey ke rakhtey hi rahengey aur chhodtey to hum kehtey : chhodey hi rahengey. aur aap ney Madina Munawra tashrif aawri (laaney) key baad Ramzanul-Mubarak key ilawa kabhi musalsal eik mahina rozey nahin rakhey.
2186,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Shaqeeq bayan kartey hain ke mainey Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) sey arz kiya : kya Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) zuhaa ki namaz padha kartey they? unhoney farmaya : nahin, magar ye ke aap safar sey wapis tashrif laeyn. mainey kaha : kya Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) kisi mahiney key mukammal rozey rakhtey they? farmaya : nahin. merey ilm key mutabiq aap ney kisi mahiney key mukammal rozey nahin rakhey ilawa Ramzanul-Mubarak key aur na kisi mahiney key tamam dino ka naagha kiya balke kuchh na kuchh zarur rozey rakhtey they yahan tak ke faut ho gaey."
2187,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Shaqeeq sey riwayat hai ke mainey Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) sey puchha : kya Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) zuhaa ki namaz padha kartey they? unhoney farmaya : nahin magar ye ke aap kisi safar sey wapis tashrif laeyn. mainey arz kiya : kya Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) Ramzanul-Mubarak key ilawa kisi moayan (taishuda) mahiney key rozey rakhtey they? unhoney farmaya : Allah ki qism ! aap ney Ramzanul-Mubarak key ilawa kisi moayan mahiney key rozey nahin rakhey yahan tak ke Allah Taala ko piyarey ho gaey aur na aap ney kisi mahiney key mukammal rozey chodey, balke kuchh na kuchh rozey rakhtey they."
2188,Hazrat Juber bin Nafeer sey manqul hai ke eik aadmi ney Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) sey (nafl) rozon key barey mein sawal kiya to unhoney farmaya : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) Shoban (key taqriban) sabhi rozey rakhtey they aur Somwar (peer) aur Jumerat ka roza qasdan rakha kartey they.
2189,Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) farmati hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) Shoban aur Ramzanul-Mubarak key mukammal rozey rakhtey they aur Somwar aur Jumerat ka roza qasdan rakhtey they.
2190,Hazrat Sila sey marwi (riwayat hui) hai ke hum Hazrat Ammaar (Raziallahu anhu) key paas they to unkey paas bhuni hui (salim) bakri laee gaee. unhoney (haazirin sey) farmaya : khao. lekin kuchh log eik taraf ho gaey aur kehney lagey : hamara roza hai. Hazrat Ammaar (Raziallahu anhu) ney farmaya : jisney shak waley din ka roza rakha us ney Hazrat Abul-Qaasim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ki nafarmani ki.
2191,"Hazrat Simaak sey riwayat hai ke main Hazrat Ikrima key paas aisey din gaya jis key barey mein shak tha ke ye Shoban ka din hai ya Ramzanul-Mubarak ka? aap roti, sabzi aur doodh tanaawul farma (kha) rahey they. mujhey kehney lagey : aao (khana khao). mainey kaha : mera to roza hai. unhoney Allah ki qism kha kar kaha ke tujhey zarur roza chhodna padeyga. mainey kaha : Subhan-Allah ! do dafa (mainey aisa kaha) jab mainey dekha ke wo In-sha-Allah padhey baghair qism kha rahey hain to main aagey badha aur arz kiya : laaiye ! jo aap key paas hai. (khana ya daleel) unhoney kaha : mainey ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) sey suna, wo bayan kar rahey they ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : chaand dekh kar rozey shuru karo aur chaand dekh kar rozey rakhney band karo. agar badal rukawat ban jaey ya andhera chha jaey. (aur chaand nazar na aaye) to Shoban key tees din purey karo. aur Ramzanul-Mubarak key shuru honey sey pehley roza na rakho aur Ramzanul-Mubarak ko Shoban key din sey (roza rakh-kar) na milaao."
2192,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) farmaya kartey they : khabrdar ! Ramzanul-Mubarak key shuru honey sey eik do din pehley roza na rakho, haan wo shakhs jo pehley sey us din ka roza rakhta tha, wo rakh ley."
2193,"Hazrat Saeed bin Musaiyab sey riwayat hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jo shakhs eman ki haalat mein aur sawab ki niyat sey Ramzanul-Mubarak (ki raaton) main nafli ibadat karey (taravih padhey) uskey sab pehley gunah maaf kar diye jaeyngey."
2194,"Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ki zauja mohtarma Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) bayan karti hain ke : bilashuba Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) logon ko Ramzanul-Mubarak (ki raaton) main nafl namaz (taravih) ki targheeb diya kartey they, baghair iskey ke unhen qatae hukm den. aap farmatey they : jo shakhs eman ki haalat mein aur sawab ki niyat sey Ramzanul-Mubarak (ki raaton) main nafl namaz (taravih) padheyga, uskey sab pehley gunah maaf kar diye jaeyngey."
2195,"Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) farmati hain ke : (eik dafa) Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) aadhi raat ko ghar sey nikal kar masjid mein namaz padhney lagey aur logon ko (nafl) namaz padhaai. aur raawi ney puri hadees bayan ki. is hadees mein ye alfaz bhi hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) logon ko qiyam Ramzan ki targheeb (dilchaspi) dilaaya kartey they, baghair iskey ke in ko is ka qatae hukm den. aur farmatey they : jo shakhs lailatul-qadr mein eman ki buniyad par aur sawab ki niyat sey nafli ibadat kerega, uskey sab pehley gunah maaf kar diye jaeyngey. raawi ney kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) faut huye to soorate-haal yehi thi (ke log umuman nafl namaz akeley akeley padhtey they. koi Imam muqarrar na tha)."
2196,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke : mainey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ko Ramzanul-Mubarak key barey mein farmatey suna : jo shakhs eman ki bina par aur sawab key husool ki niyat sey is (Ramzanul-Mubarak) ka qiyam kerega, uskey sab pehley gunah maaf kar diye jaeyngey."
2197,"Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) (Ramzanul-Mubarak key doran mein) aadhi raat ko ghar sey nikal kar masjid mein namaz padhney lagey. aur (raawi ney) puri hadees bayan ki, is mein ye bhi kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) logon ko Ramzan ke qiyaam ki targheeb (shauq) dilaaya kartey they, baghair iskey ke aap in ko is ka qatae hukm den. aap farmatey they : jo shakhs eman ki buniyad par aur sawab ki niyat sey Ramzanul-Mubarak ki raaton mein nafl namaz padheyga, uskey sab pehley gunah maaf kar diye jaeyngey."
2198,Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke mainey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ko Ramzanul-Mubarak key barey mein farmatey suna : jo shakhs eman ki bina par aur sawab ki niyat sey is ki raaton ka qiyam kerega (yani taravih padheyga) uskey sab pehley gunah maaf kar diye jaeyngey.
2199,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jo shakhs eman key sath aur sawab hasil karney key liye Ramzan mein qiyam kerega, uskey sab pehley gunah maaf kar diye jaeyngey."
2200,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) qiyame-Ramzan mein raghbat (dilchaspi) dilaaya kartey they, baghair iskey ke in ko is ka qatae hukm den. aap ney farmaya : jo shakhs eman ki haalat mein aur sawab hasil karney key liye Ramzanul-Mubarak (ki raaton) main qiyam kerega, uskey sab pehley gunah maaf ho jaeyngey."
2201,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey manqul (naqal hui) hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jis shakhs ney eman key jazbey sey aur husoole-sawab ki niyat sey Ramzanul-Mubarak (ki raaton) main nafl namaz (taravih) padhi, uskey sab pehley gunah maaf kar diye jaeyngey."
2202,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jo shakhs eman ki haalat mein aur sawab hasil karney ki gharz sey Ramzanul-Mubarak ka qiyam kerega, uskey sabiqa tamam gunah maaf kar diye jaeyngey."
2203,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey marwi hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jis shakhs ney eman ki wajeh sey aur sawab ki khatir qiyame-Ramzan kiya, uskey sab pehley gunah maaf kar diye jaeyngey."
2204,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jis shakhs ney Ramzanul-Mubarak key rozey rakhey aur qiyam kiya, eman ki bina par aur sawab ki niyat sey, to uskey sab pehley gunah maaf kar diye jaeyngey. aur jis shakhs ney eman aur ehtisaab key sath lailatul-qadr ka qiyam kiya, uskey bhi sab pehley gunah maaf kar diye jaeyngey."
2205,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey manqul (naqal hui) hai, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jo shakhs eman ki wajeh sey aur sawab hasil karney key liye Ramzanul-Mubarak key rozey rakhey, uskey sab pehley gunah maaf kar diye jaeyngey."
2206,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey marwi hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jis shakhs ney eman ki haalat mein aur husooley-sawab ki khatir Ramzanul-Mubarak key rozey rakhey, uskey sab pehley gunah maaf kar diye jaeyngey."
2207,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey marwi (riwayat hui) hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jo aadmi eman aur ehtisaab key sath Ramzanul-Mubarak key rozey rakheyga to uskey sab pehley gunah maaf kar diye jaeyngey."
2208,Hazrat Abu-Salma kehtey hain ke mujh sey Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ney bayan kiya ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jo shakhs eman key jazbey sey aur sawab ki niyat sey Ramzanul-Mubarak (ki raaton) ka qiyam kerey. uskey sab pehley gunah maaf kar diye jaeyngey. aur jo shakhs eman key jazbey sey aur sawab ki niyat sey lailatul-qadr ka qiyam kerey. uskey bhi sab pehley gunah maaf kar diye jaeyngey.
2209,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jo shakhs eman aur ehtisaab key sath Ramzanul-Mubarak ka qiyam kerega, uskey sab pehley gunah maaf kar diye jaeyngey. aur jo shakhs eman aur ehtisaab key sath lailatul-qadr ka qiyam kerega, uskey bhi sab pehley gunah maaf kar diye jaeyngey."
2210,Hazrat Nazar bin Shebaan Hazrat Abu-Salma bin Abdur-Rehman ko miley aur arz kiya : mujhey sab sey afzal hadees bayan kijiye jo aap ney apney walid mohtaram sey Ramzanul-Mubarak ki fazilat key barey mein suni ho. unhoney farmaya : mujh sey Hazrat Abdur-Rehman bin Auf (Raziallahu anhu) ney bayan kiya ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney Ramzanul-Mubarak ka zikr farmaya aur usey dusrey tamam mahinon par fazilat di aur farmaya : jo shakhs eman ki bina par aur sawab ki niyat sey Ramzanul-Mubarak (ki raaton) main qiyam kerey. wo apney gunahon sey is tarah saaf ho jata hai jis tarah wo us din tha jis din uski walida ney usey janm diya tha. Imam abu-Abdur-Rehman (Nasai) (Rahmatullahi Alaih) bayan kartey hain : ye ghalat hai. (yani Abdur-Rehman bin Auf ka zikr) durust (Abu-Salma an Abi Huraira) hai.
2211,Hazrat Abu-Salma sey Isi tarah ki riwayat aati hai jis mein ye lafz hain : jis shakhs ney eman aur ehtisaab key sath Ramzanul-Mubarak key rozey rakhey aur (raaton ka) qiyam kiya … . الخ
2212,"Hazrat Nazar bin Shebaan ney kaha : mainey Hazrat Abu-Salma bin Abdur-Rehman sey kaha : mujhey koi aisi hadees bayan kijiye jo aap ney apney walid mohtaram sey suni ho aur aap key baap ney Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) sey Ramzanul-Mubarak key barey mein bila-wasta (direct) suni ho. unhoney kaha : haan mujhey walid mohtaram ney bayan kiya ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : bilashuba Allah Taala ney tum par Ramzanul-Mubarak key rozey rakhna farz kiya hai aur mainey tumharey liye is (ki raaton) ka qiyam masnoon kiya hai, lihaza jo shakhs eman rakhtey huye aur sawab ki niyat sey is maahe-muqaddas mein siyaam (rozey) aur qiyam kerega, wo gunahon sey is tarah pak ho jaeyga jis tarah usey uski maa ney gunahon sey pak janaa tha."
2213,"Hazrat Ali bin Abi Talib (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : Allah Taala farmata hai : bilashuba roza merey liye hai aur main hi us ka badla dunga. rozey-daar key liye do waqt khushi key hain : jab wo roza kholta hai aur jab apney Rab ko milega. qism us zaat ki jis key haath mein meri jaan hai ! rozey-daar key munh ki boo Allah Taala key nazdik kastoori sey bhi ziyada achchhi hai."
2214,Hazrat Abdullah bin Masood (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Allah ney farmaya : roza merey liye hai aur main hi us ka badla dunga. rozey-daar ko do khushiyan nasib hain : eik khushi jab wo apney Rab taala sey milega aur dusri khushi iftaar key waqt. aur rozey-daar key munh ki boo Allah Taala key nazdik kastoori sey bhi badh kar khushbudar hai.
2215,"Hazrat Abu-Saeed (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : Allah Taala farmata hai : roza merey liye hai aur main hi uski haqeeqi jaza dunga. rozey-daar key liye do khushiyan hain : eik, jab wo roza kholta hai to khush hota hai. doosra jab wo Allah Taala ko milega, phir Allah usey rozey ka badla deyga to wo khush hoga. qism us zaat ki jis key haath mein Muhammad ki jaan hai ! rozey-daar key munh ki boo Allah Taala key nazdik kastoori ki khushbu sey bhi pakizah tar hai."
2216,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney (Allah taala sey hikayat kartey huye ) farmaya : roza merey liye hai aur main hi us ka badla dunga. rozey daar do dafa khush hoga : iftaar key waqt aur jab Allah Taala ko milega. aur rozey daar key munh ki boo Allah Taala key nazdik kastoori ki mehak sey bhi ziyada achchhi hai."
2217,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey manqul (naqal hui) hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : insan jo neki karta hai, wo uskey liye das guna sey saat sau guna tak likhi jati hai. Allah Taala ney farmaya : magar roza, ke wo merey liye hai aur us ka badla main hi dunga. wo meri wajeh sey apni shehwat (nafsaani khuwahish) aur khaney peeney sey dast kaash! (rokey huey) hota hai. roza dhaal hai. rozey daar key hissey mein do khushiyan hain, eik to iftaar key waqt aur dusri apney Rab sey mulaqat key waqt. aur rozey-daar key munh ki boo Allah Taala key nazdik kastoori ki khushbu sey ziyada umda hai."
2218,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey manqul (naqqal hui) hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney (Allah taala sey hikayat kartey huye ) farmaya : insan ka har amal uskey liye hai siwaye rozey key ke wo merey liye hai aur main hi us ka badla dunga. aur roza dhaal hai. jab kisi din tum mein sey kisi ka roza ho to na wo koi shahwaani (nafsaani khahish ki) baat kerey. na shor aur ghul machaey. agar koi shakhs us sey gaali galoch ya ladaai karey to wo keh dey : main rozey daar hun. qism us zaat ki jis key haath mein Muhammad ki jaan hai ! rozey daar key munh ki boo qiyamat key din Allah Taala key nazdik kastoori ki khushbu sey bhi pakizah tar hogi. rozey daar key nasib mein do khushiyan hain : jab roza kholta hai to iftaar sey khush hota hai aur jab apney Rab taala ko milega to apney rozey (ki jaza) sey khush hoga."
2219,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey marwi (riwayat hui) hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : Allah ney farmaya : insan ka har amal uskey liye hai siwaye rozey key ke wo merey liye hai aur main hi us ka badla dunga. roza dhaal hai. jab tum mein sey kisi ka roza ho to na wo koi shahwaani (nafsaani khahish ki) baat karey aur na shor aur ghul kerey. agar koi shakhs us sey gaali galoch ya ladaai karey to wo keh dey : main rozey daar hun. qism us zaat ki jis key haath mein Muhammad ki jaan hai ! rozey daar key munh ki boo Allah Taala key nazdik kastoori ki khushbu sey bhi ziyada achchhi hai. Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey Saeed bin Musaiyab ney bhi ye riwayat bayan ki hai."
2220,Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke mainey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ko farmatey suna : Allah farmata hai : insan ka har amal uskey liye hai magar roza merey liye hai aur main hi us ka badla dunga. qism us zaat ki jis key haath mein Muhammad ki jaan hai ! rozey-daar key munh ki boo Allah Taala key nazdik kastoori ki mehak sey bhi pakizah tar hai.
2221,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey marwi (riwayat hui) hai, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney Allah Taala sey bayan farmaya : har neki jo insan karta hai wo usey (sawab key lihaz sey kam se kam) das guna ho kar mileygi magar roza, ke wo merey liye hai aur main hi us ka badla dunga."
2222,Hazrat Abu-Umama (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke main Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key paas hazir huwa aur arz kiya : mujhey aisi chiz ka hukm dijiye jo main aap sey khususi taur par hasil karun (us par amal karun). aap ney farmaya : roza rakha karo kyonkey is jaisi koi chiz nahin.
2223,Hazrat Abu-Umama Bahili (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke mainey arz kiya : aey Allah key Rasool ! mujhey kisi aisi chiz ka hukm dijiye jis key sath Allah Taala mujhey bahut faeyda ata farmaey. aap ney farmaya : rozey ko mamool bana kyonkey is jaisi koi chiz nahin.
2224,Hazrat Abu Umaama (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke mainey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) sey puchha : kon sa amal afzal hai? aap ney farmaya : rozey ki aadat dal kyonkey koi aur kaam iskey barabar nahin.
2225,"Hazrat Abu-Umama (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke mainey arz kiya : aey Allah key Rasool ! mujhey kisi kaam ka hukm dijiye. aap ney farmaya : rozey rakha kar kyonkey is jaisa koi kaam nahin. mainey phir kaha : aey Allah key Rasool ! mujhey kisi aur kaam ka hukm dijiye. aap ney farmaya : rozey hi rakha kar, koi aur kaam iskey barabar nahin."
2226,"Hazrat Muaz bin Jabal (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : roza dhaal hai."
2227,"Hazrat Muaz bin Jabal (Raziallahu anhu) sey marwi (riwayat hui) hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : roza dhaal ki tarah bachao ka zariya hai."
2228,"Hazrat Muaz (Raziallahu anhu) sey manqul hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : roza dhaal hai."
2229,"Hazrat Hukm ney kaha ke mujhey is (Hazrat Muaz (Raziallahu anhu) ki ) riwayat ko apney ustaad sey suney chaalis saal ho gaey hain, phir kehtey hain : mujhey ye riwayat Muaz bin Jabal sey (Urwa key ilawa) Memoon bin Abi Shabeeb ney bhi bayan ki hai."
2230,Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : roza bachao ka saman hai.
2231,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : roza dhaal hai."
2232,Hazrat Usman bin Abi Al Aas (Raziallahu anhu) ney Hazrat Mutrif key liye doodh mangwaya taake wo usey piye to unhoney kaha : main rozey sey hun. to Hazrat Usman bin Abi Al Aas (Raziallahu anhu) kehney lagey : mainey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ko farmatey suna : roza dhaal hai jaisey tumharey paas jang mein dhaal hoti hai.
2233,Hazrat Mutrif kehtey hain ke main Hazrat Usman bin Abi Al Aas (Raziallahu anhu) key paas hazir huwa to unhoney merey liye doodh mangwaya. mainey arz kiya : bilashuba mein rozey sey hun. farmaney lagey : mainey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ko farmatey suna : roza (jahannam ki) aag sey (bachao key liye) dhaal hai jaisey tumharey paas jang mein (bachao key liye) dhaal hoti hai.
2234,Hazrat Saeed bin Abi Hind sey bhi yehi waqiyaa manqul (naqal hui) hai magar ye riwayat mursal hai.
2235,Hazrat abu-Ubaida (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke mainey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ko farmatey suna : roza dhaal hai jab tak wo (rozey daar) usey phaad na ley.
2236,"Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : roza aag sey dhaal hai. jo shakhs rozey sey ho, us din wo jihalat (badtamizi) ka koi kaam na kerey. aur agar koi doosra shakhs us sey jihalat sey pesh aaye to wo us sey gaali galoch na karey balke keh dey ke main rozey sey hun. qism us zaat ki jis key haath mein Muhammad ki jaan hai ! rozey daar key munh ki boo Allah Taala key nazdik kastoori ki mehak sey pakizah tar hai."
2237,Hazrat Abu-Ubaida (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain : roza dhaal hai ba-sharte-ke rozey-daar is ko phaad na dey.
2238,"Hazrat Sahal bin Saad (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jannat mein Rozey daaron key liye eik darwaza makhsus hai jisey Rayyan kaha jata hai. is mein inkey ilawa koi aur dakhil na hoga. jab aakhiri rozey daar dakhil ho jaeyga to darwaza band kar diya jaeyga. jo shakhs is mein dakhil hoga piyega aur jisney eik dafa pi liya, kabhi piyasa na hoga."
2239,"Hazrat Sahal (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke jannat main eik darwaza hai jisey Rayyaan kaha jata hai. qiyamat key din aelan kiya jaeyga : kahan hain rozey-daar? kya tumhen Rayyaan (sairaabi) darwazey ki khahish hai? jo us sey jannat mein dakhil hoga, kabhi piyas mehsus na kerega. jab rozey-daar dakhil ho jaeyngey, wo darwaza band kar diya jaeyga. inkey ilawa koi aur us sey dakhil na hoga."
2240,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jo shakhs Allah Taala key raastey main eik jins ki do do cheezen kharch kerega, usey jannat mein aawaz di jaeygi : aey Allah key bandey ! ye darwaza bahut achchha hai (is sey dakhil ho) jo shakhs namaz sey raghbat (dilchaspi) rakhney wala hoga, usey namaz waley darwazey sey aawaz di jaeygi. aur jo jihad ka shauq (jihad karney wala) hoga usey jihad waley darwazey sey bulaya jaeyga. aur jo sadqa karney ka aadi (sadqa deney wala) hoga. usey sadqey waley darwazey sey bulaya jaeyga. aur jo rozey ka rasiya hoga, usey baabey-Rayyaan sey dawat di jaeygi. Hazrat Abu-Bakar Siddiq (Raziallahu anhu) ney arz kiya : aey Allah key Rasool ! kisi shakhs ko zarurat nahin ke usey har darwazey sey aawazen di jaeyn, magar kya kisi ko un sab darwazon sey bhi bulaya jaeyga? Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : haan aur mujhey ummid hai ke tum bhi unhi (logon) main sey hogey."
2241,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Masood (Raziallahu anhu) farmatey hain ke hum Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key sath (Makka Mukarrama sey) nikley to hum nojawan they aur hum shaadi waghera ki wusat nahin rakhtey they. aap ney farmaya : aey nojawan logo ! nikah karo kyonkey nikah nazar ko neecha aur sharmgah ko mehfooz karney wali chiz hai. jo shakhs (faqr (ghareebi) ki wajeh sey) nikah ki taqat na rakhey, wo rozey rakha karey kyonkey roza uski shehwat (nafsaani khahish) ko kuchal deyga."
2242,"Hazrat Alqama sey manqul (naqal hui) hai ke Hazrat Abdullah bin Masood (Raziallahu anhu) Arafat mein Hazrat Usman (Raziallahu anhu) ko miley. Hazrat Usman unhen alehda ley gaey. Hazrat Usman (Raziallahu anhu) ney Hazrat ibne-Masood (Raziallahu anhu) sey kaha : kya aap ko khahish hai ke main kisi nojawan ladki sey aap ki shaadi kar dun? Hazrat Abdullah bin Masood (Raziallahu anhu) ney Hazrat Alqama ko bhi bula liya aur un sey bayan kiya ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : tum mein sey jo shakhs nikah (key kharch) ki taqat rakhta ho, usey chahiye ke wo nikah karey kyonkey nikah nazar ko neecha aur sharmgah ko mehfooz rakhney ki chiz hai. aur jo taqat na rakhey, wo rozey rakhey kyonkey roza uskey liye dhaal hai."
2243,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Masood (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : tum mein sey jo shakhs nikah (key kharch) ki taqat rakhey wo shaadi karey aur jo itni wusat (taaqat) na paey, wo rozey rakhey kyonkey roza uski shehwat (nafsaani khahish) ko kuchal deyga."
2244,"Hazrat Abdur-Rehman bin Yazid bayan kartey hain ke hum Hazrat Abdullah bin Masood (Raziallahu anhu) key paas gaey. hamarey sath Alqama, Aswad aur kuchh dusrey log bhi they. to Hazrat Abdullah bin Masood (Raziallahu anhu) ney hamein hadees bayan ki. mera khayal hai ke aap ney un (hamarey sath waley) logon ko ye hadees meri hi wajeh sey bayan farmaee kyonkey main hi un sab sey kam umr nojawan tha ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : aey nojawan logo ! tum mein sey jo shakhs nikah karney ki taqat rakhey wo zarur nikah karey kyonkey nikah nazar ko ziyada neecha aur sharmgah ko ziyada mehfooz karta hai. raawi Ali bin Haashim kehtey hain ke Aa'mash sey Ibrahim an Alqama an Abdullah ki riwayat key mutalliq sawal kiya gaya ke kya ye is (Ammara an Abdur-Rehman) jaisi hi hai? unhoney jawab diya : haan."
2245,"Hazrat Alqama bayan kartey hain ke main Hazrat ibne-Masood (Raziallahu anhu) key sath tha jabkey wo Hazrat Usman (Raziallahu anhu) key paas they. Hazrat Usman (Raziallahu anhu) ney bayan kiya, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) kuchh nojawanon key paas tashrif laye aur farmaya : tum mein sey jo maaldaar ho, wo shaadi karey kyonkey ye chiz uski nazar ko ziyada neecha aur sharmgah ko ziyada mehfooz kar deygi aur jo maaldaar na ho to uski shehwat (khahish) ka ilaj roza hai. Imam abu-Abdur-Rehman (Nasai) (Rahmatullahi Alaih) farmatey hain ke is hadees mein jo Abu-Ma'shar raawi hai, us ka naam Ziyad bin Kaleeb hai, wo bharosemand hai aur Ibrahim Nakhai ka masaahib (sathi) hai. us sey Mansoor, Mughira aur Shoba ney riwayat kiya hai. eik Abu-Ma'shar Madini hai, us ka naam Najeeh hai aur wo zaeef hai. zaeef honey key sath wo ikhtilaat (ghal-mail) ka bhi shikar ho gaya tha. wo munkir hadeesein bhi bayan karta tha. uski (bayan karda) munkir hadeeson mein sey eik wo hai jo us ney Muhammad bin Amr sey bayan ki, unhoney Abu-Salma sey aur unhoney Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : mashriq aur maghrib key darmiyan qibla hai. aur eik wo hai jo us ney Hisham bin Urwa sey riwayat ki, unhoney apney baap (Urwa) sey aur unhoney Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) sey ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : gosht ko chhuri sey mat kaato, (balke) usey daanton sey noch kar khao."
2246,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jo shakhs Allah ki raah main eik din roza rakhey, Allah Taala us eik din ki badolat uskey chehrey ko aag sey sattar saal key fasley tak door kar deyga."
2247,"Hazrat Abu-Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jo shakhs Allah Taala ki khushnoodi key liye eik din roza rakhey, Allah Taala us din ki wajeh sey uskey aur aag key darmiyan sattar saal ka fasla farma deyga."
2248,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey marwi (riwayat hui) hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jo shakhs Allah Taala key raastey main eik din roza rakhey, Allah Taala uskey chehrey ko aag sey sattar saal key fasley tak door farma deyga."
2249,"Hazrat Abu-Saeed (Raziallahu anhu) sey manqul (naqal hui) hai, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jo aadmi Allah Taala key raastey main eik din roza rakhey, Allah Taala uskey chehrey ko jahannam sey sattar saal key fasley tak door farma deyga."
2250,"Hazrat Abu-Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ko farmatey suna : jo shakhs Allah key raastey main eik din roza rakhey, Allah Taala us eik din (key rozey) ki wajeh sey uskey chehrey ko aag sey sattar saal key fasley tak door farma deyga."
2251,"Hazrat Abu-Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) sey manqul hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jo shakhs Allah Taala key raastey main eik din roza rakhey, Allah Taala us ko aag sey sattar saal key fasley tak door farma deyga."
2252,"Hazrat Abu-Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke mainey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ko farmatey suna : jo shakhs Allah tabarak aur taala key raastey main eik din roza rakhey, Allah Taala uskey chehrey ko aag sey sattar saal key fasley tak door kar deyga."
2253,"Hazrat Abu-Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) sey marwi (riwayat hui) hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jo banda Allah Taala key raastey main eik din roza rakhey, Allah Taala us eik din ki wajeh sey aag ko uskey chehrey sey sattar saal key fasley tak door farma deyga."
2254,"Hazrat Abu Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) sey marwi (riwayat hui) hai, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jo shakhs eik din Allah Taala key raastey mein roza rakheyga, Allah Taala is din ki barkat sey jahannam ki tapish ko uskey chehrey sey sattar saal key fasley tak door kar deyga."
2255,"Hazrat Abu-Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jis shakhs ney Allah Taala key raastey main eik din roza rakha, Allah Taala is din ki bina par aag ko uskey chehrey sey sattar saal key fasley tak door rakheyga."
2256,"Hazrat Aqba bin Aamir (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jo shakhs Allah key raastey main eik din roza rakhey, Allah Taala jahannam ko us sey so saal ki masafat (doori) tak door farma deyga."
2257,Hazrat Kaab bin Aasim (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke mainey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ko farmatey suna : safar mein roza rakhna neki nahin.
2258,"Hazrat Saeed bin musaiyab sey riwayat hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : safar mein roza rakhna neki nahin. Imam Abu-Abdur-Rehmaan (Nasai) (Rahmatullahi Alaih) farmatey hain ke ye ghalat hai, durust is sey pehli (sanad) hai. hamarey ilm mein nahin hai ke is par kisi ney ibne Kasir ki mutaabiat (pairwi) ki ho."
2259,Hazrat Jabir bin Abdullah (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney logon ko eik shakhs key ird-gird jama dekha to puchha (kya baat hai?) logon ney kaha : eik aadmi hai jisey rozey ki wajeh sey sakht takleef hai. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : safar key doran mein (is had tak pahunchaney wala) roza rakhna neki nahin.
2260,"Hazrat Jabir bin Abdullah (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) eik aadmi key paas sey guzrey jisey eik darkht key saye taley litaayaa gaya tha aur us (key munh) par pani key chheentey maarey ja rahey they. aap ney farmaya : tumharey is sathi ko kya huwa hai? logon ney kaha : aey Allah key Rasool ! us ney roza rakha hai. aap ney farmaya : ye neki nahin ke tum safar key doran mein (is tarah key) rozey rakho, balke jo Allah Taala ney tumhen rukhsat (chhoot) di hai, us sey faeyda uthao aur usey qubul karo."
2261,Muhammad bin Abdur-Rehman bayan kartey hain ke mujhey eik shakhs ney aisi hi hadees sunai jisney ye hadees Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) sey suni thi.
2262,"Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : safar key doran mein (us qism ka) roza rakhna neki nahin, balke Allah Taala ki rukhsat sey faeyda uthao aur usey qubul karo."
2263,"Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : safar key doran mein (mashaqqat wala) roza rakhna neki nahin."
2264,Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) sey manqul hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney eik aadmi ko dekha jis par safar key doran mein saya kya gaya tha. aap ney farmaya : safar key doran (is qism ka) roza rakhna neki nahin.
2265,Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) sey marwi hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) fateh Makka key saal Ramzanul-Mubarak mein makkey ki taraf chaley aur rozey rakhtey rahey yahan tak ke Karaa Ghameem pahunchey. logon ney roza rakha huwa tha. aapko ye baat pahunchi ke logon key liye roza nibhana mushkil ho gaya hai. ye Asr key baad ki baat hai. aap ney pani ka piyala mangwaya aur piya. log dekh rahey they. kuch logon ney to roza khol liya lekin kuch logon ney roza qaaim rakha. aap ko ye baat pahunchi ke kuch log abhi tak rozey sey hain. to aap ney farmaya : ye log nafarman hain.
2266,Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key paas «Marruz-Zohran» maqam mein khana laya gaya. aap ney Hazrat abu-Bakar aur Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) sey farmaya : qarib aao aur khao. un dono ney kaha : hum rozey sey hain. aap ney deegar sahaba Raziallahu anhum sey farmaya : apney un do mohtaram sathiyon key liye sawariyan tum tayyar karna aur unkey dusrey kaam bhi tum karna.
2267,Hazrat abu-Salma sey riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) eik dafa « Marruz-Zohran » maqam par khana kha rahey they. aap key sath Hazrat abu-Bakar o umr Raziallahu anhuma they. aap ney farmaya : tum bhi khana khao. ye riwayat mursal hai.
2268,Hazrat abu-Salma sey marwi hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) aur Hazrat abu-Bakar o umr (Raziallahu anhu) « Marruz-Zohran » maqam par they. ye riwayat bhi mursal hai.
2269,Hazrat Amr bin Umayya zamri (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke main eik safar sey wapis Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key paas hazir huwa. aap ney farmaya : aey Abu Umaiya! khana aa raha hai. zara thehro mainey arz kya : main rozey sey hun. aap ney farmaya : idhar aao. merey qarib ho taake main tumhen bataun ke Allah Taala ney musafir sey roza aur nisf namaz maaf kar di hai.
2270,"Hazrat Amr bin Umayya Zamri (Raziallahu anhu) farmatey hain ke main ( safar sey wapsi par) Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key paas aaya. mujh sey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : aey Abu Umaiya ! kya to khana aaney ka intizar nahin kerega ? mainey kaha : mera to roza hai. aap ney farmaya : idhar aao, mein tumhen bataun ke Allah Taala ney musafir sey roza aur nisf namaz maaf kar di hai."
2271,"Hazrat Abu Umaiya Zamri sey marwi hai, wo kehtey hain ke main eik safar sey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key paas wapis aaya. mainey aap ko salam arz kya. jab main uthney laga to aap ney farmaya : aey Abu Umaiya ! khana aaney tak thehro. mainey kaha : aey Allah key Nabi ! main to rozey sey hun. aap ney farmaya. idhar aao, mein tumhen bataun ke Allah Taala ney musafir sey roza aur nisf namaz maaf kar di hai."
2272,Hazrat Abu Umaiya Zamri sey riwayat hai ke main Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key paas aaya. aur uper wali hadees ki maanind hadees bayan ki.
2273,"Hazrat Abu Umaiya Zamri (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke main eik safar sey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key paas hazir huwa. aap ney farmaya : aey Abu Umaiya ! thehro khana aa raha hai. mainey arz kya : mera to roza hai. aap ney farmaya : idhar aao, mein tumhen batao ke Allah Taala ney musafir ko roza aur nisf namaz maaf kar di hai."
2274,"Hazrat Abu Umaiya Zamri (Raziallahu anhu) ney bataya ke main eik safar sey (wapsi par) Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key paas hazir huwa. main rozey sey tha. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney mujh sey farmaya : tum khaney tak nahin thehrogey? mainey arz kya : main to rozey sey hun. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : idhar aao, main tumhen bataun ke Allah Taala ney musafir ko roza aur aadhi namaz maaf kar di hai."
2275,Hazrat Abu Umaiya (Raziallahu anhu) ney khabar di ke main safar sey wapis Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key paas aaya. mazkura baala riwayat ki maanind.
2276,"Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : Allah Taala ney musafir ko aadhi namaz aur roza maaf kar diya hai. aur (isi tarah) hamila aur doodh pilaney wali aurat ko bhi."
2277,Hazrat Ayub sey manqul hai ke hamen bataya gaya ke Qusher qabiley ka eik buzurg apney sahabi chacha sey hadees bayan karta hai. ( hum gaey to ) hamney us buzurg ko uskey oonton mein paya. ( merey sath ustaad mohtaram abu-Qulaba bhi they) to Hazrat abu-Qulaba ney us ( buzurg ) sey kaha ke usey wo hadees bayan kijiye : to us buzurg ney farmaya ke mujhey merey chacha (Anas bin Malik Qusheri (Raziallahu anhu)) ney bayan farmaya ke main apney oonton (key mutalbey) key silsiley mein Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key paas pahuncha. aap us waqt khana kha rahey they. aap ney farmaya : aao aur khana khao. mainey arz kya : mera roza hai. aap ney farmaya : Allah Taala ney musafir ko nisf namaz aur roza maaf kar diya hai. isi tarah hamila aur bachey ko doodh pilaney wali ko bhi.
2278,"Hazrat Ayub bayan kartey hain ke mujhey ye hadees Hazrat abu-Qulaba ney bayan farmaai phir farmaney lagey : kya tum is hadees key raawi sey milna chahtey ho? aur mujhey unka pata bataya. main ja kar unhen mila to unhoney farmaya : mujh sey merey eik rishtey daar, jinhen Anas bin Malik (Raziallahu anhu) kaha jata hai, ney bayan kya ke main Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key paas apney oonton key mutalbey key liye hazir huwa jo ( ghalat fehmi ki bana par) pakad liye gaey they. mainey aap ko khana khatey paya. aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney mujhey khaney ki dawat di. mainey kaha : mera to roza hai. aap ney farmaya : idhar aao, main tumhen is barey mein batata hun ke Allah Taala ney musafir ko roza aur nisf namaz maaf kar di hai."
2279,"Hazrat abu Qulaba eik sahabi sey bayan kartey hain ke unhoney farmaya : main Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key paas kisi kaam key silsiley mein hazir huwa. aap subh ka khana kha rahey they. aap ney farmaya : aao khana khao. mainey arz kya : main rozey sey hun. aap ney farmaya : idhar aao, main tumhen rozey key barey mein batata hun ke Allah Taala ney musafir ko nisf namaz aur roza maaf kar diya hai. aur hamila aur doodh pilaney wali aurat ko bhi rukhsat di hai."
2280,Hazrat Abu Ala bin Shikhkhir ney bhi eik shakhs sey aisi hi riwayat bayan ki hai.
2281,"« Bal-Harish » ( Banu al-Harish ) qabiley key eik shakhs ney apney walid sey bayan kya, unhoney farmaya : main musafir tha. main Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key paas aaya. main us waqt rozey sey tha, aur aap khana kha rahey they. aap ney farmaya : tum bhi aao. mainey arz kya : mera to roza hai. aap ney farmaya : idhar aao. kya tum nahin jantey ke Allah Taala ney musafir ko maafi di hai? mainey kaha : kis chiz ki ? farmaya : rozey aur nisf namaz ki."
2282,« Bal-Harish » ( Banu al-Harish ) qabiley key eik shakhs ney apney walid mohtaram sey bayan kya ke hum safar kya kartey they jab tak Allah Taala chahta . hum Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key paas aaye to aap khana kha rahey they. farmaya : aao khana khao. mainey kaha : mera to roza hai. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : main tumhen rozey key barey mein bayan karta hun ke Allah Taala ney musafir ko roza aur aadhi namaz maaf kar di hai.
2283,Hazrat Hani bin Abdullah bin Shikhkhir apney walid mohtaram sey bayan kartey hain ke unhoney farmaya : main musafir tha. Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key paas aaya. aap us waqt khana kha rahey they. aur mera roza tha. aap ney farmaya : aao. mainey kaha : mera to roza hai. farmaya : kya tum jantey ho ke Allah Taala ney musafir ko kya maaf kya hai? mainey kaha : Allah Taala ney musafir ko kya maaf kya hai? aap ney farmaya : roza aur nisf namaz.
2284,"Hazrat Ghelan bayan kartey hain ke main Hazrat abu-Qulaba key sath eik safar mein gaya. unhoney khana merey qarib kya. mainey kaha : mera to roza hai. wo kehney lagey ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) (eik dafa) safar mein nikley. aap ney khana qarib kya aur eik aadmi sey farmaya : aao ! khana khao. us ney kaha : main to rozey sey hun. aap ney farmaya : Allah Taala ney musafir ko nisf namaz aur roza safar mein maaf kar diya hai, lihaza tum qarib aao aur khao. ( Ghelan ney kaha : ) (ye hadees sun kar) mein qarib huwa aur mainey khana khaya."
2285,"Hazrat Anas bin Malik (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke hum Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key sath safar mein they. kisi ney roza rakha huwa tha, kisi ney nahin rakha tha. ye sakht garm din they. hum utrey aur saya hasil kya. rozey daar to let gaey lekin roza na rakhney waley uthey aur unhoney hamari sawaariyon key janweron ko pani pilaya. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : aaj to roza na rakhney waley sawab ley gaey."
2286,Hazrat Abdur-Rehman bin Auf (Raziallahu anhu) farmatey hain : kaha jata hai ke safar mein roza rakhna ghar mein reh kar roza na rakhney key barabar hai.
2287,Hazrat Abdur-Rehman bin Auf (Raziallahu anhu) ney farmaya : safar mein roza rakhney wala ghar reh kar roza na rakhney waley ki tarah hai.
2288,Hazrat Abdur-Rehman bin Auf (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke safar mein roza rakhney wala ghar reh kar roza na rakhney waley ki tarah hai.
2289,Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) sey manqul hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) Ramzanul-Mubarak mein ( fateh Makka key liye) nikley. aap rozey rakhtey rahey yahan tak ke «Quded» maqam par aaye to aap key paas doodh ka piyala laya gaya. aapney piya aur sahaba samet roza khol liya.
2290,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ney farmaya : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) Madina Munawra sey chaley to rozey rakhtey rahey yahan tak ke qudaid key maqam par aa gaey, phir aap ney rozey rakhney band kar diye yahan tak ke Makka Mukarrama aa gaey."
2291,Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ( fateh Makka key) safar mein rozey rakhtey rahey yahan tak ke qudaid maqam par aaye to doodh ka piyala mangwaya aur pi liya. is tarah aap ney aur aap key sahaba ney roza khol liya.
2292,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ( fateh Makka key waqt ) Makka Mukarrama ko chaley to rozey rakhtey rahey yahan tak ke Asfan maqam par pahunchey to piyala mangwaya aur pi liya. aur ye Ramzanul-Mubarak ki baat hai. Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) (is bana par) farmaya kartey they : ( safar mein) jo shakhs chahey roza rakhey, jo chahey na rakhey."
2293,Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) sey marwi hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney Ramzanul-Mubarak mein (fateh Makka ka) safar kya. rozey rakhtey rahey yahan tak ke maqam Asfan mein pahunchey to bartan mangwaya aur abhi din hi tha ke aap ney pi kar roza khol liya. sab log aapko dekh rahey they.
2294,Hazrat Awam bin Hoshab sey riwayat hai ke mainey Hazrat Mujahid sey safar mein roza rakhney key barey mein puchha to unhoney farmaya : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) (safar key doran mein) roza rakh bhi letey they aur chhod bhi detey they.
2295,Hazrat Mujahid sey riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney safar key doran mein maah Ramzanul-Mubarak key rozey rakhey bhi hain aur chodey bhi.
2296,"Hazrat Hamza bin Amr Aslami (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke mainey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) sey safar key doran mein roza rakhney key barey mein puchha. aap ney farmaya, agar to chahey to rakh ley aur chahey to na rakh."
2297,Hazrat Suleman (Alaihissalam) bin Yasar sey riwayat hai ke Hazrat Hamza bin Amr ney kaha : aey Allah key Rasool ! phir usi key misl bayan kya. ye riwayat mursal ( munqata) hai.
2298,Hazrat Hamza Aslami (Raziallahu anhu) sey manqul hai ke mainey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) sey dorane-safar mein roza rakhney key barey mein puchha to aap ney farmaya : agar to roza rakhna chahey to roza rakh ley aur agar na rakhna chahey to na rakh.
2299,Hazrat Hamza bin Amr (Raziallahu anhu) sey marwi hai ke mainey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) sey safar ki haalat mein roza rakhney key barey mein puchha to aap ney farmaya : to roza rakhna chahey to roza rakh sakta hai. na rakhna chahey to chhod bhi sakta hai.
2300,"Hazrat Hamza bin Amr Aslami (Raziallahu anhu) ney arz kya : aey Allah key Rasool ! yaqinan main safar ki haalat mein roza rakhney ki taqat rakhta hun (to kya main roza rakh liya karun ) aap ney farmaya : agar chahey to rakh ley, chahey to na rakh."
2301,Hazrat Hamza bin Amr (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke mainey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) sey dorane-safar mein roza rakhney key barey mein puchha. aap ney farmaya : agar roza rakhna chahey to rakh ley aur agar na rakhna chahey to na rakh.
2302,"Hazrat Hamza bin Amr (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke main Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key daur mein lagatar nafl rozey rakha karta tha to mainey arz kya : aey Allah key Rasool! main safar mein bhi lagataar rozey rakh leta hun (koi harj to nahin?) aap ney farmaya : chahey to roza rakh, chahey to na rakh."
2303,"Hazrat Hamza ( Aslami) (Raziallahu anhu) farmatey hain ke mainey arz kya : aey Allah key Rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ! main musalsal nafl rozey rakhta hun to kya safar mein bhi roza rakh liya karun? aap ney farmaya : ji chahey to rakh ley, ji chahey to na rakh."
2304,"Hazrat Hamza bin Amr (Raziallahu anhu) ney jo ke safar mein rozey rakha kartey they, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) sey (is barey mein) puchha to aap ney farmaya : chahey to roza rakh, chahey to na rakh."
2305,"Hazrat Hamza bin Amr (Raziallahu anhu) sey manqul hai, unhoney Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) sey arz kya : main apney aap mein dorane-safar mein roza rakhney ki taqat paata hun to kya roza rakhney mein mujh par koi gunah hai? aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : roza na rakhna Allah azz-w-jall ki taraf sey rukhsat hai. jo rukhsat par amal karey to achi baat hai aur jo roza rakhna chahey to is par bhi koi gunah nahin."
2306,Hazrat Hamza bin Amr Aslami (Raziallahu anhu) sey marwi hai ke main safar mein rozey rakha karta tha. (us liye) mainey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) sey puchha : kya main dorane-safar mein roza rakh sakta hun? aap ney farmaya : agar to chahey to roza rakh ley aur agar chahey to na rakh.
2307,Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai ke Hazrat Hamza bin Amr Aslami ney kaha : aey Allah key Rasool ! main aksar nafl rozey rakhta hun to kya safar mein bhi rakh liya karun ? aap ney farmaya : agar chahey to roza rakh ley aur agar chahey to na rakh.
2308,Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai ke Hazrat Hamza ( Aslami ) (Raziallahu anhu) ney Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) sey arz kya : aey Allah key Rasool ! main safar mein roza rakh liya karun ? aur wo aksar ( nafl ) rozey rakha kartey they. to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney un sey farmaya : agar chahey to roza rakh ley aur chahey to na rakh.
2309,"Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) farmati hain ke Hazrat Hamza (Aslami) (Raziallahu anhu) ney Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) sey sawal kya, kaha : aey Allah key Rasool! kya main safar mein roza rakh liya karun? aap ney farmaya : agar ji chahey to roza rakh ley aur agar ji chahey to na rakh."
2310,Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) sey manqul hai ke Hazrat Hamza Aslami (Raziallahu anhu) ney Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) sey dorane-safar roza rakhney key barey mein sawal kya aur ye ( Allah key bandey) lagatar nafl rozey rakha kartey they. aap ney farmaya : agar to chahey to roza rakh ley aur agar chahey to chhod dey.
2311,Hazrat abu-Saeed (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke hum Ramzanul-Mubarak mein safar kya kartey they. koi hum mein sey rozey daar hota tha aur kisi ka roza nahin hota tha. na rozey daar roza chhodney waley par aetraz karta tha aur na roza chhodney wala rozey daar par.
2312,"Hazrat abu-Saeed (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke hum Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key sath safar kya kartey they. hum mein sey koi roza rakhta tha, koi nahin rakhta tha. na to roza rakhney wala, na rakhney waley par aetraz karta tha aur na roza na rakhney wala roza rakhney waley par koi aetraz karta tha."
2313,"Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) farmatey hain ke hamney Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key sath safar kya. hum mein sey kisi ney roza rakha tha, kisi ney nahin."
2314,"Hazrat abu-Saeed aur Hazrat Jabir Raziallahu anhuma sey manqul hai ke hamney Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key sath safar kiye. koi roza rakhta tha, koi nahin rakhta tha. na rozeydar roza chhodney waley par aetraz karta tha aur na roza chhodney wala roza daarpar."
2315,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) fateh Makka waley saal Ramzanul-Mubarak mein rozey rakhtey huye gaey, yahan tak ke jab maqam kudaid mein pahunchey to (us din ka) roza khol liya."
2316,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney ( fateh Makka ka) safar kya to rozey rakhtey gaey yahan tak ke Asfan maqam par pahunchey to bartan mangwaya aur din khadey piya taake log bhi aap ko dekh lein (aur roza khol lein). phir aap ney rozey nahin rakhey yahan tak ke Makka Mukarrama pahunch gaey aur Makka fatah kar liya. ye Ramzanul-Mubarak ki baat hai. Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) farmatey hain Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney safar mein roza rakha bhi hai aur kabhi nahin bhi rakha, lihaza jo shakhs chahey roza rakhey, jo chahey na rakhey."
2317,Hazrat Anas bin Malik Qusheri (Raziallahu anhu) sey manqul hai ke main Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key paas Madina Munawra aaya. aap khana tanaawul farma rahey they. aap ney mujh sey farmaya : aao khana khao. mainey arz kya : main rozey sey hun. Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : Allah Taala ney musafir ko roza aur nisf namaz maaf farma di hai. aur hamila aur bachey ko doodh pilaney wali ko bhi.
2318,"Hazrat Salma bin akwa (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke jab ye aayat utri : « { وَ عَلَی . . . . . . طَعَامُ مِسْکِیْنٍ }  jo log rozey ki taqat rakhtey hain wo fidya den eik miskeen ka khana. to hum mein sey jo shakhs rozey na rakhna chahta, wo fidya dey deta yahan tak ke uskey baad wali aayat utri aur us ney usey mansookh kar diya."
2319,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) sey Allah Taala key farman : « { وَ عَلَی الَّذِیْنَ یُطِیْقُوْنَہٗ فِدْیَۃٌ طَعَامُ مِسْکِیْنٍ } » key barey mein manqul hai ke is aayat mein « { یُطِیْقُوْنَہٗ } » sey murad hai ke jo log intehai mashaqqat mehsus karen (yani intehai boodhey jinki sehat ki ummid nahin) wo (roza rakhney key bajaey) eik miskeen ka khana bator fidya den. aur us sey agley alfaz « { فَمَنْ تَطَوَّعَ خَیْرًا فَھُوَ خَیْرٌ لَّہٗ }  jo shakhs khushi sey neki karey to achi baat hai. sey murad hai ke jo shakhs eik sey zayed miskeen ka khana fidye mein dey dey to ye bahut achcha hai. to (us maana key lihaz sey) ye aayat mansookh nahin. aur (intehai mashaqqat key bawajood) koi shakhs roza rakhey to behtar hai, lihaza roza chhodney aur fidya deney ki rukhsat sirf us shakhs ko hai jo (intehai budhapey ki wajeh sey) roza bardasht nahin kar sakta. ya wo mareez jiski sehat ki koi ummid nahin."
2320,"Hazrat Muaza Adwiya sey manqul hai ke eik aurat ney Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) sey puchha : kya haiz wali aurat pak honey key baad namaz ki qaza ada keregi ? Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ney farmaya : kya to khariji aurat hai? hamen bhi Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key daure-masood mein haiz aata tha, phir hum pak hoti thin to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) hamen rozon ki qaza ada karney ka hukm to detey they magar namaz ki qaza ada karney ka hukm nahin detey they."
2321,"Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) farmati hain ke mujh par Ramzanul-Mubarak key kuch rozey (haiz ki wajeh sey) wajibul-ada reh jatey they to main unki qaza ada nahin kar sakti thi, yahan tak ke Shoban aa jata tha."
2322,"Hazrat Muhammad bin saifi (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney Aashura (das Moharramul Haram) key din farmaya : kya tum mein sey kisi ney aaj khana khaya hai? logon ney arz kya : kuch logon ney roza rakha hai aur kuch ney nahin. aap ney farmaya : phir baqi din kuch na khana, neez Madina Munawra key qurb o jawar bastiyon mein pegham bhej do ke wo baqi din kuch na khaeyn piyen."
2323,"Hazrat Salma (Raziallahu anhu) sey marwi hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney eik aadmi ko Ashura key din hukm diya ke aelan karo : jisney kuch kha liya hai, wo baqi din na khaye piye aur jisney kuch nahin khaya, wo roza rakh ley."
2324,"Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) farmati hain ke eik din Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) merey paas tashrif laye aur farmaya : kya tumharey paas koi khaney ki chiz hai? mainey kaha : nahin. aap ney farmaya : chalo main roza rakh leta hun. phir kisi aur din merey paas sey guzrey. ittifaaq se us waqt mujhey hees ka tohfa aaya huwa tha aur mainey aap key liye kuch rakh chhoda tha. aap hees ko bahut pasand farmatey they. mainey arz kya : aey Allah key Rasool ! hamarey paas hees ka tohfa aaya hai aur mainey aap key liye kuch mehfooz rakha huwa hai. aap ney farmaya : lao pesh karo. mainey to aaj rozey ki niyat kar rakhi thi. phir aap ney wo hees khaya aur farmaya : nafl rozey ki misal aisi hai jaisey aadmi apney maal sey sadqa nikaley, phir chahey usey kharch kar dey, chahey apney paas rakh ley."
2325,"Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) farmati hain ke eik dafa Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney merey paas chakkar lagaya aur farmaya : tumharey paas koi khaney ki chiz hai? mainey arz kya : merey paas koi chiz nahin hai. aap ney farmaya : phir main roza rakh leta hun. phir ( kisi din ) dobara tashrif laye. ittifaaq se hamarey paas hees ka tohfa aaya tha. main aap key paas laee to aap ney kha liya. mujhey is par tajjub huwa. mainey kaha : aey Allah key Rasool ! aap tashrif laye to aap ka roza tha, phir aap ney hees kha liya ? aap ney farmaya : Aaisha ! haan. Ramzan ya qazaey Ramzan key ilawa nafl rozey rakhney waley ki misal to us shakhs ki tarah hai jisney apney maal ka sadqa nikala to jis qadr chaha kharch kar diya aur uska sawab hasil kar liya aur jitna chaha kanjusi kartey huye rakh liya."
2326,Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) bayan karti hain ke kabhi Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) tashrif latey aur farmatey : tumharey paas khana hai? main arz karti ke nahin. aap farmatey : main roza rakh leta hun. aap eik din hamarey paas tashrif laye. ittifaaq se hamarey paas hees ka tohfa aaya tha. aap ney farmaya : koi khaney ki chiz hai? mainey arz kya : ji haan. hees ka tohfa aaya huwa hai. aap ney farmaya : aaj meri niyat rozey ki thi. phir aap ney ( hees ) kha liya. Qasim bin Yazid ney (apney sathi abu-Bakar ki ) mukhalifat ki hai.
2327,Hazrat Aaisha ummul-Mominin (Raziallahu anha) farmati hain ke eik din Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) merey paas tashrif laye. mainey kaha : hamarey paas hees ka tohfa aaya hai. mainey aap ka hissa sanbhaal kar rakha huwa hai. aap ney farmaya : tehqiq mainey rozey ki niyat ki hui thi. phir aap ney roza khatam kar diya.
2328,"ummul-Mominin Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai ke kabhi-kabhi Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) merey paas tashrif latey. aapka roza hota. aap farmatey : tumharey paas khaney ki koi chiz hai? mein kehti : nahin. aap farmatey : chalo, mera roza hai. phir uskey baad eik din aaye to mainey kaha : aaj hamarey paas tohfa aaya hai. aap ney farmaya : kya? mainey kaha : hees. aap ney farmaya : mainey aaj subh rozey ki niyat ki thi. phir aap ney kha liya."
2329,ummul-Mominin Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) sey marwi hai ke eik din Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) merey paas tashrif laye aur farmaya : tumharey paas ( khaney ki ) koi chiz hai? hamney kaha : nahin. aap ney farmaya : main roza rakh leta hun.
2330,"Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) sey manqul hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) merey paas tashrif laye aur farmaney lagey : tumharey paas khana hai? hamney kaha : nahin. aap ney farmaya : phir mera roza hai. phir eik aur din tashrif laye. mainey kaha : aey Allah key Rasool ! hamarey paas hees ka tohfa bheja gaya hai. aap ney mangwaya, phir farmaya : bilashuba mainey aaj subh rozey ki niyat ki thi. phir aap ney kha liya."
2331,Hazrat Mujahid aur umme-Kulsum sey marwi hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) key yahan tashrif ley gaey aur farmaya : tumharey paas kuch khana hai? baqi riwayat sabiqa riwayat ki tarah hai. Imam abu-Abdur-Rehman ( Nasai) (Rahmatullahi Alaih) bayan kartey hain ke Samaak bin Harab ney us riwayat ko « an رجل an عائشۃ bint Talha » key tareeq sey bayan kya hai. ( yani aadmi ko mubham rakha hai. agli hadees Samaak hi ki hai.)
2332,ummul-Mominin Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) sey marwi hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) eik din tashrif laye aur farmaya : tumharey paas koi khana hai? mainey kaha : nahin. aap ney farmaya : to phir main roza rakh leta hun. Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) kehti hain ke phir eik aur dafa aap tashrif laye to mainey arz kya : aey Allah key Rasool! hamarey yahan hees ka tohfa aaya hai. aap ney farmaya : to phir aaj main roza khol leta hun. wesay mainey rozey ki niyat ki hui thi.
2333,"Hazrat Hafsa (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jo shakhs tulu Fajr sey pehley raat key waqt rozey ki niyat na karey to uska roza nahin hota."
2334,"Hazrat Hafsa (Raziallahu anha) sey manqul hai, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jo shakhs tulu Fajr sey qabl raat ko rozey ki niyat na kerey. us ka roza nahin hota."
2335,"Hazrat Hafsa (Raziallahu anha) sey marwi hai, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jis shakhs ney tulu Fajr sey pehley rozey ki niyat na ki, wo roza na rakhey."
2336,Hazrat Hafsa (Raziallahu anha) sey bayan hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jo shakhs raat key waqt rozey ki niyat na kerey. us ka roza nahin.
2337,Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Hazrat Hafsa (Raziallahu anha) farmaya karti thin : jo shakhs raat key waqt rozey ki niyat na kerey. wo roza na rakhey.
2338,"Hazrat Hafsa (Raziallahu anha) jo ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ki zauja mutahra thin, unhoney farmaya is aadmi ka roza nahin hota jo tulu Fajr sey pehley rozey ki niyat na kerey."
2339,Hazrat Hafsa (Raziallahu anha) farmati hain ke us shakhs ka roza nahin hota jo Fajr sey pehley rozey ki niyat nahin karta.
2340,"Hazrat Hafsa (Raziallahu anha) farmati hain ke jo shakhs tulu Fajr sey pehley rozey ki niyat nahin karta, us ka roza nahin."
2341,"Hazrat Hafsa (Raziallahu anha) sey marwi hai ke jo shakhs Fajr sey pehley rozey ka azm nahin karta, uska roza nahin hota."
2342,Hazrat Hafsa (Raziallahu anha) farmati hain is shakhs ka roza nahin hota jo tulue-Fajr sey pehley rozey ki niyat nahin karta. Imam Malik (Rahmatullahi Alaih) ney us riwayat ko mursal (munqata) bayan kya hai.
2343,"Hazrat Aaisha aur Hazrat Hafsa (Raziallahu anha) sey usi key misl marwi hai, unhoney farmaya : wo shakhs roza na rakhey jisney tulue-Fajr sey qabl rozey ki niyat nahin ki."
2344,Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke jab koi shakhs raat ko rozey ki niyat na karey to wo roza na rakhey.
2345,Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) farmaya kartey they : rozey na rakhey magar wo shakhs jisney tulu Fajr sey pehley rozey ki niyat kar li.
2346,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Amr bin Aas (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : Allah azz-w-jall ko sab sey ziyada pasandida rozey Dawud alehissalam key rozey hain. wo eik din roza rakhtey they aur eik din nahin rakhtey they. aur Allah Taala ko ziyada pasandida nafl namaz bhi Dawud alehissalam ki (raat ki ) namaz hai. wo aadhi raat tak sotey they, phir eik tihai raat namaz padhtey aur aakhiri chata hissa phir so jatey they."
2347,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) farmatey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ayyame-beez (chaandni raaton waley dino) ka roza nahin chhodtey they, chahey ghar mein hotey ya safar mein."
2348,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) sey marwi hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) (kabhi-kabhi nafl) rozey musalsal rakhtey yahan tak ke hum kehtey they ke aap chodengey nahin aur phir chhodna shuru farmatey yahan tak ke hum kehtey : aap rakhengey nahin, jab sey aap Madina tashrif laye aap ney kabhi bhi Ramzanul-Mubarak key ilawa eik maah musalsal rozey nahin rakhey."
2349,Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) farmati hain : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) rozey rakhtey jatey yahan tak ke hum kehtey : aap kisi bhi din roza chhodney ka irada nahin rakhtey. aur phir chhodney lagtey yahan tak ke hum kehtey : aap kisi bhi din roza rakhney ka irada nahin rakhtey.
2350,Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) bayan karti hain ke merey ilm mein nahin ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney eik raat mein sara Quran Majeed padha ho ya sari raat subh tak nafl namaz padhtey rahey hon ya Ramzanul-Mubarak key ilawa kisi mahiney key mukammal rozey rakhey hon.
2351,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Shaqeeq sey riwayat hai ke Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) sey Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key ( nafl ) rozon key barey mein puchha gaya to unhoney farmaya : kabhi aap us qadr rozey rakhtey ke hum kehtey : aap rozey rakhtey hi rahengey aur kabhi us qadr naghey farmatey ke hum kehtey : aap ney rozey mustaqilan chhod diye hain. aur aap jab sey Madina Munawra tashrif laye, aap ney Ramzanul-Mubarak key ilawa kisi bhi mahiney key mukammal rozey nahin rakhey. (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam)۔"
2352,Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) sey marwi hai ke rozey rakhney key liye Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ka sab sey ziyada pasandida mahina Shoban tha. balke aap taqriban usey Ramzanul-Mubarak sey mila hi detey they.
2353,"Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) farmati hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) rozey rakhtey jatey yahan tak ke hum kehtey : aap chodengey nahin. aur aap rozey chhodney lagtey to hum kehtey : rakhengey nahin, aur mainey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ko Shoban sey ziyada kisi mahiney mein rozey rakhtey nahin dekha."
2354,Hazrat Umme-Salma (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) Shoban o Ramzan key ilawa do mahiney musalsal rozey nahin rakhtey they.
2355,Hazrat Umme-Salma (Raziallahu anha) sey marwi hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) Shoban key ilawa saal bhar key kisi mahiney mein mukammal (nafl) rozey nahin rakhtey they. Shoban ko to aap taqriban Ramzanul-Mubarak key sath hi mila detey they.
2356,Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) farmati hain Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) Shoban sey ziyada kisi mahiney mein rozey nahin rakhtey they. Shoban key mahiney mein aap aksar rozey rakha kartey they.
2357,Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) sey marwi hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) Shoban key rozey rakha kartey they. sirf chand din nagha farmatey they.
2358,Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) bayan karti hain ke beshak Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) (taqriban) mukammal Shoban key rozey rakha kartey they.
2359,"Hazrat Usama bin Zaid (Raziallahu anhu) sey manqul hai ke mainey ( Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) sey) arz kya : aey Allah key Rasool ! mainey aap ko kisi mahiney mein itney rozey rakhtey nahin dekha jitney aap Shoban mein rakhtey hain. (kya wajeh hai?) aap ney farmaya : ye wo mahina hai ke rajab aur Ramzanul-Mubarak key darmiyan aaney ki wajeh sey log us sey ghaflat kar jatey hain, halanke ye wo mahina hai ke is mein rabbul-Alameen key yahan insanon key aamal pesh kiye jatey hain. mein chahta hun ke merey amal pesh hun to main rozey sey hun."
2360,"Hazrat Usama bin Zaid (Raziallahu anhu) sey manqul hai ke mainey kaha : aey Allah key Rasool ! aap kabhi is qadr rozey rakhtey hain ke lagta hai aap chodengey nahin aur kabhi is qadr chhodtey hain ke lagta hai rakhengey nahin, magar do dino ka zarur rakhtey hain. aap key (umumi) rozon mein aa jaeyn to fabiha, warna aap unka roza khususan rakhtey hain. aap ney farmaya : kon sey do din? mainey kaha : somwar aur jumerat. aap ney farmaya : ye do din aisey hain ke un main rabbul-Alameen key yahan aamal pesh hotey hain aur main chahta hun ke merey amal pesh hun to main rozey sey hun."
2361,Hazrat Usama bin Zaid (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) kabhi-kabhi lagataar rozey rakhtey they yahan tak ke kaha jata : aap chodengey nahin aur kabhi chhodney lagtey yahan tak ke kaha jata : aap rakhengey nahin.
2362,"Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : tehqiq Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) somwar aur jumerat ka roza qasdan rakha kartey they."
2363,"Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) Somwar aur Jumerat ka roza koshish sey rakha kartey they."
2364,"Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) sey marwi hai, farmaya : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) Somwar aur Jumerat ka roza khususan rakhtey they."
2365,"Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) sey manqul hai, farmaya : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) Somwar aur Jumerat key din roza iraade ke saath rakha kartey they."
2366,"Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) sey marwi hai, unhoney farmaya : Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) Somwar aur Jumerat key din ka roza rakha kartey they."
2367,Hazrat Umme-Salma (Raziallahu anha) sey marwi hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) har mahiney mein teen din roza rakhtey they : do eik haftey mein pair aur Jumerat ko aur agley haftey key peer ko.
2368,Hazrat Hafsa (Raziallahu anha) farmati hain Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) har mahiney Jumerat aur Somwar ko aur dusrey Juma ( haftey ) sey Somwar ko roza rakhtey they.
2369,"Hazrat Hafsa (Raziallahu anha) sey manqul hai, unhoney farmaya : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) jab bistar par lettey they to apna daayan haath mubarak (hatheli) apney daain rukhsaar key nichey rakhtey they aur Somwar aur Jumerat ka roza rakha kartey they."
2370,Hazrat Abdullah bin Masood (Raziallahu anhu) sey marwi hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) har mahiney key shuru sey teen din ka roza rakhtey they aur Juma Mubarak key din kam hi roza chhodtey they.
2371,Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai unhoney farmaya : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney mujhey hukm diya ke main Zuha (chaasht) ki do rakatein padha karun aur baghair witr padhey na soun aur har mahiney mein teen rozey rakhun.
2372,"Hazrat Ubedullah bayan kartey hain ke mainey suna jabkey Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) sey Aashura key rozey key barey mein puchha gaya, aap ney farmaya : main to nahin janta ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney kisi din ko dusrey dino sey afzal samajh kar uska roza rakha ho, siwaye us din key, yani Aashura aur maah Ramzanul-Mubarak key."
2373,"Hazrat Humed bin Abdur-Rehman bin Auf bayan kartey hain ke mainey Hazrat Muawiya (Raziallahu anhu) ko Aashura key din member nabawi par farmatey suna : aey Madiney walo! kahan gaey tumharey ulama? mainey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ko us din key barey mein farmatey suna : mainey aaj roza rakha huwa hai, to jo roza rakhna chahey, wo rakh ley."
2374,"Hazrat Hanida bin Khalid ki zauja mohtarma sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : mujh sey Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ki kisi zauja mohtarma ney bayan farmaya ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) Aashura Moharram, zul-hijja key pehley no din aur har mahiney key teen din, mahiney ka pehla Somwar aur do ibtidaai Jumeratein roza rakha kartey they."
2375,"Hazrat Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu anhu) sey manqul hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jisney bila nagha roza rakha uska koi roza nahin."
2376,"Hazrat Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jisney hamesha roza rakha, to (aisey samjho ke) us ney na roza rakha aur na iftaar kya (woh be roza raha)."
2377,"Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) sey marwi hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jisney hamesha roza rakha, uska roza nahin."
2378,"Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) sey manqul hai, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jisney hamesha roza rakha ( samjho ) us ney roza nahin rakha."
2379,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Amr bin Aas (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jisney har roz roza rakha, us ney roza rakha, na chhoda."
2380,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Amr bin Aas (Raziallahu anhu) ney kaha : Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ko ye baat pahunchi ke main lagataar rozey rakhta hun. aur raawi hadees ney puri hadees bayan ki. ibn juraij bayan kartey hain ke Ata farmatey hain ke mujhey malum nahin ke hamesha roza rakhney waley alfaz is qissey mein kaisey aagey (albatta Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ka ye farman mujhey yad hai ke aap ney farmaya:) padhi. jisney hamesha roza rakha, us ka roza nahin hota."
2381,Hazrat Imran (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ko batlaya gaya : falan shakhs kabhi bhi rozey sey nagha nahin karta. aap ney farmaya : na us ney roza rakha aur na chhoda.
2382,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Shikhkhir (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) sey suna jab aap key paas eik aadmi ka zikr huwa jo bila nagha rozey rakha karta tha. aap ney farmaya is ney na roza rakha aur na chhoda."
2383,Hazrat Abdullah bin Shikhkhir (Raziallahu anhu) sey marwi hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney hamesha roza rakhney (waley) key barey mein farmaya : usney na roza rakha aur na chhoda.
2384,Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke hum Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key sath they ke hum eik aadmi key paas sey guzrey. logon ney kaha : aey Allah key Nabi! ye shakhs itney arsey sey rozey ka nagha nahin kar raha. aap ney farmaya : na usney roza rakha aur na chhoda.
2385,"Hazrat abu-Qatada (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) sey aap key rozon key barey mein puchha gaya to aap naraz ho gaey. Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) ney arz kya : hum Allah Taala key rab honey, Islam key Deen honey aur Hazrat Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key Rasool honey par razi hain, phir aap sey us shakhs key barey mein puchha gaya jo bila nagha rozey rakhta tha. aap ney farmaya is ney na roza rakha aur na chhoda."
2386,Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai ke Hazrat Hamza bin Amr Aslami (Raziallahu anhu) ney Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) sey puchha : aey Allah key Rasool! main lagatar rozey rakhta hun to kya safar mein bhi rakh liya karun? aap ney farmaya : agar to chahey to rakh ley aur agar chahey to na rakh.
2387,Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key eik sahabi (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) sey kaha gaya ke eik aadmi hamesha rozey rakhta hai. aap ney farmaya : kaash! wo kabhi khana na khata (aur mar jata ). logon ney arz kya : do tihai dino key rozey kaisey hain? aap ney farmaya : ye bhi bahut ziyada hain. unhoney kaha : nisf dino key rozey ? aap ney farmaya : ye bhi ziyada hi hain. phir farmaya : main tumhein wo rozey na bataun jo seeney ka keena ( dil key mafasid ) door karney key liye kafi hain? har maah mein teen din key rozey.
2388,Hazrat Amr bin Shurehbil (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke eik shakhs Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key paas aaya aur kehney laga : aey Allah key Rasool ! aap us aadmi key barey mein kya farmatey hain jo hamesha roza rakhta hai? Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : main to chahta hun ke wo kabhi kuch na khata. us ney kaha : do tihai rozey ? aap ney farmaya : bahut ziyada hain. us ney kaha : nisf dino key rozey ? aap ney farmaya : ye bhi ziyada hi hain. aap ney farmaya : main tumhen aisey rozon ki khabar na dun jo dil ki kharabiyon ( akhlaqi kamzoriyon ) ko door kar detey hain? logon ney kaha : kyon nahin ( zarur bataiye ) aap ney farmaya : har mahiney main teen rozey.
2389,"Hazrat abu-Qatada (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) ney arz kya : aey Allah key Rasool ! us shakhs key barey mein kya irshad hai jo hamesha bila nagha roza rakhta hai? aap ney farmaya is ney na roza rakha aur na chhoda. unhoney arz kya : aey Allah key Rasool! us shakhs key barey mein kya hukm hai jo do din roza rakhta hai, eik din nagha karta hai? aap ney farmaya : kya koi shakhs ( hamesha ) uski taqat rakh sakta hai? unhoney phir arz kya is shakhs key barey mein kya farman hai jo eik din roza rakhta hai, eik din nagha karta hai? aap ney farmaya : ye to Hazrat Dawud alehissalam ka roza hai. unhoney arz kya is shakhs key barey mein kya raey hai jo eik din ka roza rakhta hai, do din iftaar karta hai? aap ney farmaya : meri khahish hai ke mujhey uski taqat hoti . phir farmaya : har mahiney mein teen rozey rakh lena aur har Ramzan key rozey rakh lena ( sawab key lihaz sey) zamana bhar key rozey rakh leney key barabar hai."
2390,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Amr (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : afzal tareen rozey Dawud alehissalam key rozey hain. wo eik din roza rakhtey aur eik din nagha farmatey they."
2391,"Hazrat Mujahid bayan kartey hain ke Hazrat Abdullah bin Amr (Raziallahu anhu) ney mujh sey farmaya ke merey walid ney eik sahibe rutba (aali nasab) khatoon sey mera nikah kar diya, phir wo (aksar) uskey paas aa kar uskey khawind key (yani merey) barey mein poochhtey to wo khatoon kehti : badey achchhey aadmi hain jo kabhi merey bistar par nahin aaye aur jab sey main aai hun, kabhi mera pehlu talash nahin kiya. merey walid ney ye baat Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) se ki to aap ney farmaya : usey ley kar merey paas aana. main unkey sath aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key paas hazir huwa to aap ney farmaya : tum rozey (nafl) kaisey rakhtey ho? mainey arz kiya : har roz. aap ney farmaya : har haftey sey teen din rozey rakho. mainey arz kiya : main is sey ziyada ki taqat rakhta hun. aap ney farmaya : do din roza rakho aur eik din nagha karo. mainey arz kiya : main is sey bhi ziyada ki taqat rakhta hun. aap ney farmaya : Dawud alehissalam ki tarah rozey rakho jo afzal tareen rozey hain. eik din roza, eik din naagha."
2392,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Amr (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke merey walid ney eik khatoon sey meri shaadi kar di, phir wo us sey milney aaye to puchha : tera khawind kaisa hai? wo kehney lagi : achchha aadmi hai jo raat ko sota nahin aur din ko rozey sey nagha nahin karta. to walid mohtaram ney mujhey sakht sust kaha aur farmaney lagey ke mainey eik (behtareen) musalman aurat sey teri shaadi ki hai aur tu ney usey bin biyaahi bana rakha hai? lekin mein unkey kehney ki taraf tawajjoh nahin deta tha kyonkey main apney andar (ibadat ki) quwat aur shoq paata tha. ye baat Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ko pahunchi to aap ney farmaya : lekin main to raat ko namaz bhi padhta hun aur sota bhi hun. roza bhi rakhta hun aur naghey bhi karta hun, chunanche to namaz bhi padh aur so bhi. rozey bhi rakh aur naghey bhi kar. aap ney farmaya : har mahiney sey teen rozey rakh liya kar. mainey arz kiya : mujhey is sey ziyada ki taqat hai. aap ney farmaya : phir Dawud alehissalam jaisey rozey rakh. eik din roza rakh aur eik din nagha kar. mainey kaha : mujhey is sey ziyada ki taqat hai. (magar aap ney ijazat na di), phir aap ney farmaya : eik maah mein (tahajjud key doran mein) eik dafa Quran khatam kiya kar. lekin phir (merey bar-bar kehney par) aap pandarah tak aa gaey. main ab bhi yehi keh raha tha : mujhey is sey zayed ki taqat hai."
2393,"Hazrat Abdullah (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) merey hujrey mein tashrif laye aur farmaney lagey : kya mujhey ye bataya nahin gaya ke to sari raat namaz padhta rehta hai aur har din roza rakhta hai? mainey arz kiya : ji han, aap ney farmaya : aisey na kar. so bhi aur qiyam bhi kar. roza bhi rakh aur nagha bhi kar. yaqinan teri aankh ka tujh par haq hai, terey jism ka tujh par haq hai, teri biwi ka tujh par haq hai, terey mehman ka bhi tujh par haq hai aur terey dost ka bhi tujh par haq hai. ummid hai teri umr lambi hogi, lihaza tujhey ye kafi hai ke har mahiney sey teen rozey rakh liya kar. ye (sawab key lihaz sey) zamaney bhar key rozon key barabar ho jaeyngey kyonkey har neki ka badla das guna hai. mainey arz kiya : main ziyada taqat rakhta hun. mainey apney aap par sakhti ki to mujh par sakhti dal di gaee. aap ney farmaya : har haftey mein teen rozey rakh liya kar. mainey kaha : main is sey ziyada ki taqat rakhta hun. is tarah mainey apney aap par sakhti ki to mujh par sakhti dal di gaee. aap ney farmaya : Allah key Nabi Hazrat Dawud alehissalam ki tarah roza rakh liya kar. mainey kaha : Hazrat Dawud alehissalam key rozey kaisey they? aap ney farmaya : nisf zamana (yani eik din roza eik din nagha)."
2394,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Amr bin Aas (Raziallahu anhu) ney farmaya ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key samney meri baat zikr ki gaee ke main sari raat ibadat kiya karunga aur har din roza rakha karunga jab tak bhi zinda raha. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : to ye baat kehta hai? mainey arz kiya : aey Allah key Rasool ! yaqinan mainey ye baat kahi hai. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : to is ki taqat nahin rakh sakeyga, lihaza roza rakh aur nagha bhi kar, so bhi aur ibadat bhi kar. aur har mahiney mein teen din rozey rakh liya kar. chunkey neki ka badla das guna hai, lihaza ye (sawab key lihaz sey) hamesha rozey rakhney ki tarah ho jaeyngey. mainey kaha : main is sey ziyada ki taqat rakhta hun. aap ney farmaya : phir eik din roza rakh aur do din nagha kar. mainey kaha : main is sey ziyada ki taqat rakhta hun. aap ney farmaya : phir eik din roza rakh aur eik din nagha kar. aur ye Hazrat Dawud alehissalam key rozey hain aur ye afzal tareen rozey hain. mainey kaha : main is sey afzal ki taqat rakhta hun. aap ney farmaya : is sey afzal koi roza nahin. Hazrat Abdullah bin Amr (Raziallahu anhu) farmatey hain ke main wo teen rozey hi qubul kar leta jo Allah key Rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney merey liye tajwiz farmaai they to (ab) ye mujhey merey ehal aur maal sey ziyada pasand aur mehbub hota."
2395,"Hazrat Abu-Salma bin Abdur-Rehman sey riwayat hai, main Hazrat Abdullah bin Amr (Raziallahu anhu) key paas gaya aur kaha : chacha jaan ! mujhey wo baat bayan farmaiye jo Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney aap ko irshad farmaee thi. wo farmaney lagey : aey bhateejey ! mainey ye azm (pakka irada) kiya tha ke main ibadat mein sakht mehnat karunga yahan tak ke mainey kaha : main hamesha rozey rakhunga aur eik din raat mein pura Quran Majeed khatam kiya karunga. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney (kisi sey) ye baat sun li to aap merey paas tashrif laye yahan tak ke merey ghar mein dakhil ho gaey aur farmaney lagey : mujhey pata chala hai ke tu ney kaha hai : main hamesha roza rakha karunga aur (har roz) pura Quran (namaz mein) padha karunga. mainey arz kiya : aey Allah key Rasool ! bilashuba mainey ye baat kahi hai. aap ney farmaya : aisey na karna. har mahiney mein teen rozey rakh liya kar. mainey arz kiya : main is sey ziyada ki taqat rakhta hun. aap ney farmaya : phir haftey mein do din, yani Somwar aur Jumerat ka roza rakh liya kar. mainey kaha : main is sey bhi ziyada ki taqat rakhta hun. aap ney farmaya : phir Hazrat Dawud alehissalam jaisey rozey rakha kar kyonkey wo Allah Taala key nazdik behtareen (aur munasib tareen) rozey hain. eik din roza aur eik din nagha aur Hazrat Dawud alehissalam jab waada farma letey they to khilaf warzi na kartey they aur jab dushman sey muqabla hota to bhagtey na they."
2396,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Amr (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney mujh sey farmaya : eik roza rakh liya kar, baqi dino ka sawab bhi tujhey mil jaeyga. mainey kaha : mujhey is sey zayed ki taqat hai. aap ney farmaya : do din roza rakh liya kar, baqi dino ka sawab bhi tujhey mil jaeyga. mainey kaha : mujhey is sey zayed ki taqat hai. aap ney farmaya : teen din roza rakh liya kar, baqi dino ka sawab bhi tujhey mil jaeyga. mainey kaha : mujhey is sey zayed ki taqat hai. aap ney farmaya : chaar din roza rakh liya kar, baqi dino ka sawab bhi tujhey mil jaeyga. mainey arz kiya : mujhey is sey bhi zayed ki taqat hai. aap ney farmaya : to Hazrat Dawud alehissalam key rozey rakha kar jo Allah Taala key nazdik afzal tareen rozey hain. wo eik din roza rakhtey they aur eik din nagha farmatey they."
2397,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Amr (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke mainey Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key samney rozey ka zikr kiya to aap ney farmaya : har das din main eik din roza rakh liya kar, baqi no din ka sawab bhi tujhey mil jaeyga. mainey kaha : mujh mein is sey ziyada ki taqat hai. aap ney farmaya : phir har no din main eik roza rakh liya kar, tujhey baqi aath dino ka sawab bhi mil jaeyga. mainey kaha : mujh mein mazeed taqat hai. aap ney farmaya : har aath din main eik din roza rakh liya kar, tujhey baqi saat din ka sawab bhi mil jaeyga. mainey kaha : mujh mein us sey bhi ziyada taqat hai. aap mazeed izafa farmatey rahey yahan tak ke aap ney farmaya : eik din roza rakh aur eik din nagha kar."
2398,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Amr (Raziallahu anhu) sey marwi hai, mujh sey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : eik din roza rakh. tujhey das rozon ka sawab milega. mainey kaha : aur ziyada keejiye. aap ney farmaya : do din roza rakh ley, tujhey no rozon ka sawab milega. mainey kaha : mazeed ziyada keejiye. aap ney farmaya : teen din key rozey rakh ley, tujhey aath rozon ka sawab milega. (raawi hadees) Sabit ney kaha : mainey Hazrat Mutrif sey ye hadees bayan ki to unhoney kaha : mera khayal hai amal badh raha hai, sawab kam ho raha hai. hadees key alfaz Muhammad (bin Ismail) key bayan karda hain (Zakariya bin Yahya key nahin)."
2399,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Amr (Raziallahu anhu) sey manqul (naqal hui) hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney mujh sey farmaya : mujhey ye baat pahunchi hai ke to sari raat qiyam karta hai aur har roz roza rakhta hai. mainey arz kiya : aey Allah key Rasool ! mera irada to neki hi ka hai. aap ney farmaya : jo hamesha roza rakhey, us ka koi roza nahin, lekin main tujhey hamesha key rozey ka eik tariqa batata hun : mahiney mein teen rozey rakh (sawab purey mahiney key barabar hoga). mainey kaha : aey Allah key Rasool ! main is sey ziyada ki taqat rakhta hun. aap ney farmaya : (mahiney mein) paanch din roza rakh. mainey kaha : main is sey ziyada ki taqat rakhta hun. aap ney farmaya : phir das rakh. mainey kaha : main is sey ziyada ki taqat rakhta hun. aap ney farmaya : Hazrat Dawud alehissalam key rozey rakha kar. wo eik din roza rakhtey they aur eik din nagha farmatey they."
2400,"Hazrat Abul-Abbaas ney jo ke Sham key rehney waley shayer they. (bawajood shayer honey key) bahut sachchey shakhs they, Hazrat Abdullah bin Amr (Raziallahu anhu) sey bayan kiya ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney mujh sey farmaya aur phir hadees bayan farmaee."
2401,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Amr (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney mujh sey farmaya : aey Abdullah bin Amr ! to hamesha rozey rakhta hai aur sari sari raat ibadat karta hai. aur jab to aisey kerega, teri aankhen andar ko dhans jaeyngi aur tabiyat thak jaeygi. us shakhs ka koi roza nahin jisney hamesha roza rakha. hamesha roza rakhney ka jayez tariqa ye hai ke har mahiney sey teen din roza rakha jaey. ye (sawab key lihaz sey) zamaney bhar ka roza ban jaeyga. mainey kaha : main is sey zayed ki taqat rakhta hun. aap ney farmaya : Hazrat Dawud alehissalam key rozey rakh. wo eik din roza rakhtey they aur eik din nagha kartey they. aur jab dushman ka samna hota tha to bhagtey na they."
2402,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Amr (Raziallahu anhu) sey manqul hai, mujh sey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : mahiney main eik dafa Quran Majeed khatam kiya kar. mainey kaha : main is sey zayed ki taqat rakhta hun. is tarah main bar-bar aap sey mazeed mutalba karta raha yahan tak ke aap ney farmaya : paanch din mein khatam kar liya kar. aap ney farmaya : mahiney mein teen rozey rakha kar. mainey kaha : mujhey is sey zayed ki taqat hai. is tarah main aap sey bar-bar mutalba karta raha yahan tak ke aap ney farmaya : Dawud alehissalam ki tarah rozey rakh jo Allah Taala ko sab sey ziyada pasandida hain. wo eik din roza rakhtey they aur eik din iftaar kartey they."
2403,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Amr bin Aas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ko ye baat pahunchi ke main lagataar rozey rakhta hun aur sari sari raat namaz padhta rehta hun. aap ney mujhey bula bheja, ya main aap ko mila (ya aap mujhey miley) aap ney farmaya : kya mujhey ye nahin bataya gaya ke to musalsal rozey rakhta hai, kabhi nagha nahin karta, aur sari sari raat namaz padhta rehta hai? aisey na kar. teri aankh ko us ka haq (neend) milna chahiye aur terey jism ko us ka haq (aaram aur khurak) milna chahiye aur teri biwi ko bhi us ka haq (shabb basri) milna chahiye. rozey bhi rakh, naghey bhi kar, namaz bhi padh aur neend bhi puri kar. har das din main eik din roza rakh. baqi no din ( key rozon ka sawab bhi tujhey mil jaeyga. mainey arz kiya : aey Allah key Rasool ! mujh mein is sey ziyada taqat hai. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : tab Hazrat Dawud alehissalam ki tarah rozey rakh. mainey kaha : aey Allah Taala key Nabi ! Hazrat Dawud alehissalam kis tarah rozey rakhtey they? aap ney farmaya : wo eik din roza rakhtey they aur eik din nagha kartey they aur jab dushman sey muqabla hota to bhagtey na they. mainey kaha : aey Allah key Nabi ! merey liye is (aakhiri) baat ka kon zaamin hoga? (yani ye bahut mushkil kaam hai, roza bhi aur jihad bhi.)"
2404,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Amr (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney bayan farmaya ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key samney merey musalsal rozey rakhney ka zikr huwa. aap merey paas tashrif laye. mainey aap key liye eik darmiyana sa chamdey ka gaddaa bichhaya jis mein khajoor ki chhaal bhari hui thi lekin aap zamin hi par beth gaey aur wo gaddaa merey aur aap key darmiyan reh gaya. aap ney farmaya : tujhey har mahiney sey teen rozey kafi nahin? mainey arz kiya : aey Allah key Rasool ! (mazeed ijazat dijiye . aap ney farmaya : paanch rozey. mainey kaha : aey Allah key Rasool ! (mazeed). aap ney farmaya : saat rozey. mainey kaha : aey Allah key Rasool ! (kuchh aur). aap ney farmaya : no rozey. main phir bola : aey Allah key Rasool ! (kuchh aur ). aap ney farmaya : giyara rozey. mainey phir kaha : aey Allah key Rasool ! (kuchh aur). to Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : Hazrat Dawud alehissalam key rozon sey badh kar koi roza nahin, yani nisf zamana ke eik din roza aur eik din nagha."
2405,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Amr (Raziallahu anhu) ka bayan hai ke mujh sey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : mahiney main eik roza rakh ley, tujhey baqi dino ka sawab mil jaeyga. mainey kaha : mujhey is sey ziyada ki taqat hai. farmaya : phir do din roza rakh ley, tujhey baqi dino ka sawab mil jaeyga. mainey arz kiya : mujhey is sey ziyada ki taqat hai. aap ney farmaya : phir teen din roza rakh ley, tujhey baqi dino ka sawab mil jaeyga. mainey arz kiya : mujhey is sey ziyada ki taqat hai. aap ney farmaya : chaar din roza rakh ley. tujhey baqi dino ka sawab mil jaeyga. mainey kaha : mujhey is sey ziyada ki taqat hai. to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : afzal tareen roza Hazrat Dawud alehissalam ka roza hai. wo eik din roza rakhtey they aur eik din nagha kartey they."
2406,"Hazrat Abu-Zar (Raziallahu anhu) farmatey hain ke mujhey merey piyarey Habib (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney teen baaton ki nasihat farmaai aur In-sha-Allah main unhein kabhi nahin chhodunga : mujhey nasihat farmaee ke namaze-zuha padha karun, witr padh kar soun aur har mahiney sey teen rozey rakhun."
2407,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) farmatey hain ke mujhey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney teen chizon ka hukm diya : witr padh kar sona, Juma Mubarak key din ghusl karna aur har mahiney sey teen din rozey rakhna."
2408,Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ney farmaya : mujhey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney hukm diya ke chaasht ki do rakatein padha karun aur witr padhey baghair na soun aur har mahiney sey teen din key rozey rakha karun.
2409,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey marwi hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney mujhey witr padh kar soney, Juma Mubarak key din ghusl karney aur har mahiney sey teen din rozey rakhney ka hukm diya."
2410,Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke mainey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ko farmatey suna ke sabr ka mahina (yani Ramzanul-Mubarak) aur har mahiney sey teen rozey (sawab key lihaz sey) zamaney bhar key rozon key barabar hain.
2411,"Hazrat Abu-Zar (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jo shakhs har mahiney teen rozey rakhey to yun samjho us ney zamaney bhar key rozey rakh liye. phir farmaya : Allah Taala ney apni kitab Quran Majeed mein sach farmaya hai : (مَنْ جَآءَ بِالْحَسَنَۃِ فَلَہٗ عَشْرُ أَمْثَالِھَا),''jo shakhs neki kerega usey (us neki ka) das guna sawab diya jaeyga''"
2412,Hazrat Abu-Zar (Raziallahu anhu) sey marwi (riwayat hui) hai ke mainey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ko farmatey suna : jo shakhs har mahiney sey teen rozey rakhey to goya mahiney bhar key rozey ho gaey (ya usey mahiney bhar key rozon ka sawab milega).
2413,Hazrat Usman bin Abul-Aas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke mainey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ko farmatey suna : achchhey rozey har maah mein teen rozey hain.
2414,Hazrat Saeed bin Abi Hind bhi Hazrat Usman bin Abul-Aas (Raziallahu anhu) sey mazkura baala riwayat ki misl (tarah) bayan kartey hain. ye riwayat mursal (munqata') hai.
2415,Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) har maah teen din roza rakhtey they.
2416,Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) har maah teen din roza rakha kartey they. mahiney ki pehli Somwar aur Jumerat ko aur phir agli Jumerat ko.
2417,"Hazrat Hanida Khuzaai sey riwayat hai ke main Ummul-Mominin (Hazrat Hafsa (Raziallahu anha)) ki khidmat mein hazir huwa. mainey suna aap farma rahi thin : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) har maah teen din roza rakha kartey they : mahiney ki pehli Somwar ko, phir Jumerat ko, phir agli Jumerat ko."
2418,"Hazrat Hafsa (Raziallahu anha) farmati hain ke chaar kaam Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) kabhi nahin chhodtey they : Aashura (10 moharram) ka roza, zul-hijja key pehley ashrey (yani no din) key rozey, har mahiney sey teen din key rozey aur namaz Fajr sey pehley do rakaten."
2419,"Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ki kisi zauja mohtarma (biwi) sey riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) zul-hijja key no din, Aashura key din aur har mahiney sey teen din (yani pehla somwar (peer) aur iskey baad wali do jumraaten) roza rakhtey they."
2420,Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ki koi zauja mohtarma (paak biwi) bayan karti hain ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ushra zul-hijja (yani no din) aur har mahiney sey teen din roza rakhtey they : (pehla) Somwar ko aur uskey baad Jumerat ko (yani do jumraaten).
2421,"Hazrat Umme-Salma (Raziallahu anha) farmati hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) (har mahiney mein) teen din key rozon ka hukm detey they, yani mahiney ki pehli Jumerat aur do somwar."
2422,"Hazrat Jareer bin Abdullah (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : har mahiney teen rozey rakhna ( sawab key lihaz sey) zamaney bhar key rozon key barabar hai. aur ayyaame beez (chamakti raaton waley din) tehra, chaudah aur pandarah hain."
2423,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke eik erabi (dehati) bhuna huwa khargosh ley kar Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key paas aaya aur usey aap key samney rakh diya. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney haath rok liya aur na khaya aur logon sey kaha ke wo kha len. erabi (dehati) ney bhi haath rokey rakha. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : tujhey khaney mein kya rukawat hai? us ney kaha ke main har mahiney mein teen din rozey rakhta hun. aap ney farmaya : agar rozey rakhney hon to chaandni raaton (key dino) key (yani chaand ki 13, 14 aur 15 taareekh ko) rozey rakha kar."
2424,"Hazrat Abu-Zar (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney hamein hukm diya ke hum har mahiney mein ayyaame beez (roshan raaton key dino) key teen rozey rakha keren, yani (chaand ki) tehra, chaudah aur pandarah taareekh ko."
2425,"Hazrat Abu-Zar (Raziallahu anhu) farmatey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney hamein har maah teen roshan (raaton key) dino key rozey rakhney ka hukm diya, yani tehra chaudah aur pandarah ko."
2426,"Hazrat Musa bin Talha bayan kartey hain ke mainey rabzaa basti mein Hazrat Abu-Zar (Raziallahu anhu) sey suna, wo farma rahey they ke mujh sey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jab to mahiney mein kuchh dino key rozey rakhey to (chaand ki) tehra, chaudah aur pandarah taareekh ko rakh."
2427,"Hazrat Abu-Zar (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney eik aadmi sey farmaya : (chaand ki) . tehra, chaudah aur pandarah taareekh key rozey rakha kar. Imam Abu-Abdur-Rehman (Nasai) (Rahmatullahi Alaih) bayan kartey hain ke ye ghalati hai. ye hadees bayan ki nahin hai, ho sakta hai ke Hazrat Sufiyan ney « حَدَّثَنَا اِثْنَانِ » kaha ho, Alif gir gaya aur kisi raawi ney ghalati sey usey bayan padh liya."
2428,"Hazrat Abu-Zar (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney eik aadmi ko tehra, chaudah aur pandarah taareekh key rozey rakhney ka hukm diya."
2429,"Hazrat ibne Hautakiya sey riwayat hai ke merey walid (Raziallahu anhu) ney farmaya ke eik erabi (dehati) Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key paas hazir huwa. uskey paas bhuna huwa khargosh tha aur rotiyaan bhi thin. us ney ye sab kuchh Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key samney rakh diya, phir kaha : mainey isey is haalat mein paya tha ke ye (is ka gosht) khoon aalud tha. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney apney sahaba sey farmaya : koi harj nahin, khao. aur aap ney erabi (dehati) sey farmaya : to bhi kha. us ney kaha : mera to roza hai. aap ney farmaya : kaisa roza? us ney kaha : mahiney key teen rozey. aap ney farmaya : agar tu ney ye rozey rakhney hon to chaandni raaton key dino key rozey rakha kar, yani tehra, chaudah aur pandarah taareekh ko. Imam Abu Abdur-Rehman Nasai (Rahmatullahi Alaih) ney farmaya : sahih baat ye hai ke ye riwayat ibne Hautakiya ney Hazrat Abu-Zar (Raziallahu anhu) sey suni hai, shayad kisi kaatib sey lafz « zar » (likhney sey) reh gaya hai aur us ney « abi » keh diya hai."
2430,"Hazrat Musa bin Talha sey riwayat hai ke eik shakhs Nabi akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key paas ( bhuna huwa ) khargosh ley kar aaya. Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney uski taraf haath badhaya hi tha ke laney waley shakhs ney kaha ke mainey iskey sath khoon dekha tha. to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney apna haath rok liya aur sahaba ko khaney ka hukm diya. wahan eik shakhs alag betha tha. Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : to kyon nahin khata? us ney kaha : mera roza hai. Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : to chaandni raaton : tehra, chaudah aur pandarah (taareekh) key rozey kyon nahin rakhta?"
2431,"Hazrat Musa bin Talha sey marwi hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key paas eik khargosh laya gaya jisey eik shakhs ney bhoonaa tha. jab us ney usey aap key samney pesh kiya to kehney laga : aey Allah key Rasool ! mainey iskey sath khoon dekha tha to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney usey chhod diya aur na khaya, albatta haazirin sey farmaya : tum khao. agar mujhey khahish hoti to kha leta. eik aadmi alag betha raha. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : to bhi qarib ho kar logon key sath kha ley. us ney kaha : aey Allah key Rasool ! main rozey sey hun. aap ney farmaya : tu ney chaandni raaton waley rozey kyon na rakh liye. us ney kaha : wo kon sey hain? aap ney farmaya : tehra, chaudah aur pandarah (taareekh key)."
2432,Hazrat Abdul-Malik apney walid sey bayan kartey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) chaandni raaton waley teen dino key rozey rakhney ka hukm detey they aur farmatey they : ye teen rozey (sawab key lihaz sey) mahiney bhar key rozon key barabar hain.
2433,Hazrat Abdul-Malik bin Abu-Minhaal apney walid sey bayan kartey they ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney sahaba kiram Raziallahu anhu ko chaandni raaton waley teen dino key rozey rakhney ka hukm diya. aur farmaya : ye mahiney bhar key rozon key barabar hain.
2434,"Hazrat Abdul-Malik bin Qudaama bin Milhaan ney apney walid sey bayan kiya ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) hamein chaandni raaton waley dino key rozon ka hukm diya kartey they, yani (chaand ki) tehra, chaudah aur pandarah (taareekh) ka."
2435,"Hazrat Abu Aqrab (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke mainey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) sey nafl rozey key barey mein puchha to aap ney farmaya : mahiney main eik roza rakh liya kar. mainey arz kiya : aey Allah key Rasool ! badhaaiye badhaaiye. aap ney (meri baat dohraatey huye) farmaya : aey Allah key Rasool ! badhaaiye badhaaiye. chalo mahiney mein do din roza rakh liya kar. mainey phir kaha : aey Allah key Rasool ! badhaaiye badhaaiye, main apney aap ko taqatwar mehsus karta hun. aap ney (meri baat dohraatey huye) farmaya : aey Allah key Rasool ! badhaaiye badhaaiye, main apney aap ko taqatwar mehsus karta hun. phir Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) khamosh ho gaey yahan tak ke mainey samjha ke aap meri darkhaast radd kar dengey. aakhir aap ney farmaya : har mahiney mein teen rozey rakh liya kar."
2436,"Hazrat Abu Aqrab (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) sey nafl rozey key barey mein puchha to aap ney farmaya : mahiney main eik roza rakh liya kar. mainey mazeed ijazat maangi aur kaha : merey maa baap aap par fidaa hon ! main apney aap ko taqatwar mehsus karta hun. aap ney mazeed ijazat dey di. aur farmaya : har mahiney do rozey rakh liya kar. mainey kaha : aey Allah key Rasool ! merey maa baap aap par qurban ! main apney aap ko taqatwar samajhta hun. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney (meri baat dohraatey huye) farmaya : main apney aap ko taqatwar samajhta hun. main apney aap ko taqatwar samajhta hun. ummid nahin thi ke aap mazeed ijazat farmaeyngey. jab mainey israr kiya to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : har mahiney teen rozey rakh liya kar."
